	 ('Zacharias Buckel','45773 Haas Point','1991-11-12','ywarland1@cornell.edu','Sooji Ordinary/Bombay Rava','Sooji Ravva is a staple in the Indian diet. It’s nutritious and can be easily digested. It has a rich flavour and aroma and provides essential amino acids for complete protein. It comes to use as the key ingredient in different dishes as it is used in a variety of soups, salads, sweets and savouries, Sooji Ravva is essential in every household. It is rich in fiber and very wholesome. It makes you stronger and is ideal for people who are managing their weight.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',20,'2022-09-22',NULL,'in progress','Yetta Warland','90764 Towne Junction','1998-01-26','ywarland1@umn.edu'),
	 ('Row Mansel','48 Lighthouse Bay Crossing','1997-02-17','asecretan2@twitter.com','HandMade Women Pink Alexa Super Skinny Fit High-Rise Clean Look Stretchable Cropped Jeans','Pink coloured wash 5-pocket high-rise cropped jeans, clean look, no fade, has a button and zip closure, and waistband with belt loops','clothes',7,'2022-06-25',NULL,'delivery','Angel Secretan','38 Cody Circle','2002-12-01','asecretan2@slate.com'),
	 ('Jeanelle Healing','575 Graedel Park','1999-03-25','csprason3@soup.io','Multigrains Atta/Godihittu','The HandMade multigrain atta is an amazing combination of six natural grains which provide wholesome nutrition to the body. The rotis and chapattis made from multigrain atta are not only tasty but extremely nutritious as well.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',64,'2022-09-05','2022-09-06','done','Clemmie Sprason','76 Vahlen Hill','1997-02-09','csprason3@naver.com'),
	 ('Ashley Hiorn','2248 Muir Park','2004-03-10','apanniers4@merriam-webster.com','HandMade Men Brown & Off-White Slim Fit Printed Casual Shirt','Brown and off-white printed casual shirt, has a spread collar, long sleeves, button placket,  curved hem, one patch pocket','clothes',27,'2022-10-30',NULL,'in progress','August Panniers','6463 Hanover Hill','2003-05-22','apanniers4@soup.io'),
	 ('Bronnie Fussell','8 Straubel Plaza','1990-02-02','rbrammar5@histats.com','Select Atta/Godihittu','HandMade is known for its high-quality grains and other products. HandMade, as a brand, believes in bringing the best grains from the country and placing them on your table in a clean, hygienic and high-quality package. HandMade Select Atta is also produced in a similar way so that you can enjoy rotis, wraps and paranthas.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',52,'2022-05-23',NULL,'delivery','Rodge Brammar','86061 Eagle Crest Trail','2003-09-08','rbrammar5@hubpages.com'),
	 ('Noby Chaudron','691 American Point','1999-03-11','ppetofi6@imdb.com','HandMade Men Blue Slim Fit Checked Casual Shirt','Blue checked casual shirt, has a spread collar, long sleeves, button placket,  curved hem, one patch pocket','clothes',37,'2022-09-10',NULL,'created','Perle Petofi','49 Blackbird Street','1990-08-07','ppetofi6@canalblog.com'),
	 ('Johnathon Greenard','135 Lakeland Street','1998-07-13','cdimitriades7@ow.ly','Besan/Kadale Hittu','Gram flour or besan is a pulse flour made from ground yellow gram lentil. It is a staple ingredient in the cuisine of the Indian. Besan or gram flour contains healthy unsaturated fats & are a good source of fiber. Ideal for mixing with flour for rotis & parathas or indulging your sweet tooth.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',38,'2022-09-14',NULL,'in progress','Catina Dimitriades','0613 Clove Plaza','1996-12-23','cdimitriades7@soup.io'),
