	 ('Willamina Duquesnay','85120 Holmberg Hill','2000-06-15','pdangl9@sitemeter.com','Sooji - Ordinary, 1 kg + Besan Flour, 1 kg + Maida, 1 kg','The BB Royal Sooji or semolina is packed with health benefits. It is actually anything but ordinary because it has been sourced from the finest of durum wheat and then packaged hygenically so that it doesnt get affected by humidity.
