	 ('Dorella Chritchlow','640 Buena Vista Park','2003-12-20','bcorkishf@cam.ac.uk','Roasted Sooji/Rava','Rava is made of semolina which is a healthy option. It’s nutritious and can be easily digested. has a rich flavour and aroma and provides essential amino acids for complete protein. Used in a variety of soups, salads, sweets and savouries, Sooji Ravva is essential in every household. This rava can be directly used in cereals, puddings & sweet dishes like halwa and salty dishes such as dosa, idly, upma, uttapam and vada. It can also be used as a dietary supplement. It has been in the market for more than five decades. It offers various food products across a variety of categories.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',48,'2022-08-01',NULL,'in progress','Bastien Corkish','10 Tomscot Terrace','1993-07-14','bcorkishf@webeden.co.uk'),
	 ('Pooh Minguet','261 Corscot Avenue','1996-07-17','rduxburyg@craigslist.org','HandMade Gold-Toned & White Solid Handcrafted Table Lamp with Shade','Type: Handcrafted Table Lamp with ShadeColour: Gold-Toned and whitePattern: SolidShape: FrustumShade material: FabricBase material: AluminiumBulb Holder Type: E27Switch Type: Toggle ButtonComes with bulb','clothes',39,'2022-09-13',NULL,'in progress','Raul Duxbury','8 Weeping Birch Road','1995-04-23','rduxburyg@fc2.com'),
	 ('Ruthi Sentance','2734 Homewood Park','1992-02-09','wfleayh@youtu.be','Organic - Ragi Flour/Ragi Hittu','Organic Ragi flour is fresh, untreated and healthy. It is a most wanted of calorie conscious people as it is super low on calories. It is a high-quality source of calcium and iron. It is free from synthetic chemicals and pesticides.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',4,'2022-06-06','2022-06-07','done','Wilfred Fleay','4087 Kinsman Drive','1992-07-13','wfleayh@free.fr'),
	 ('Willy Legan','70173 Golf View Drive','1998-07-19','rovingtoni@miibeian.gov.cn','HandMade Men Camel Brown Solid Polo Collar T-shirt','Camel brown solid T-shirt, has polo collar, short sleeves','clothes',63,'2022-06-22',NULL,'in progress','Renata Ovington','798 Summerview Alley','1996-08-03','rovingtoni@webs.com'),
	 ('Terza Tribe','68 Laurel Lane','2000-01-02','nparrissj@dell.com','Wheat Broken/Dalia','Broken Wheat is a coarsely ground cereal with various health benefits. Broken wheat commonly is used to make upma, porridge and in desserts such as pudding. Naturally, low in gluten and has a low glycemic index. Highest mineral, antioxidant and fiber content of any wheat flour. Naturally rich in fiber, vitamins like Vitamin B, Vitamin C and Vitamin E and minerals like Zinc, Calcium, Iron, Magnesium, Phosphorus, Copper, Selenium and other nutrients such as folic acid, protein, Omega3 and Omega6. It is a high-protein diet, but unlike meat items it does not contain any fat and is good for a healthy lifestyle.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',90,'2022-07-20',NULL,'delivery','Naomi Parriss','8654 Bultman Place','1992-08-27','nparrissj@examiner.com');
