	 ('Gena Crighten','9192 Karstens Parkway','1993-09-25','kvernonp@cdbaby.com','Organic - Jowar Flour/Jolada Hittu','Jowar flour is a healthy atta and gluten-free. It has a higher content of protein. It is rich in anti-oxidants, Vitamin E & B complex. Rotis made by jowar flour are soft. In India, it is used to make jowar ki roti in villages as well as urban areas. It is high in magnesium, calcium and calories. It is free of synthetic chemicals and pesticides.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',97,'2022-10-16',NULL,'in progress','Kizzie Vernon','21432 Namekagon Lane','2002-07-14','kvernonp@bluehost.com'),
	 ('Clo Applin','61377 Nevada Plaza','1993-10-16','kargileq@auda.org.au','HandMade Multicoloured Geometric 210TC Cotton 1 King Bedsheet with 2 Pillow Covers','Set content: 1 King bedsheet with 2 pillow coversQuality: Fine Thread count: 210Colour: MulticolouredPattern: Geometric','clothes',93,'2022-08-17',NULL,'in progress','Karola Argile','7 Utah Lane','1993-05-12','kargileq@mapy.cz'),
	 ('Sauncho Darlaston','2 Brentwood Parkway','1993-07-02','awalchr@google.co.jp','Organic - Besan/Kadale Hittu','Organic Besan (Gram) Flour is a good ingredient in an Indian kitchen. Besan is a ground form of chickpeas also known as chana dal. BB Royal Organics Besan is prepared of organic chickpeas and is better than any other. Apart from being an essential food ingredient, it is an efficient facial exfoliate. Besan is rich in carbohydrate and protein.Moreover, it is in nature produced and free from any injurious chemicals.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',65,'2022-12-16',NULL,'delivery','Amos Walch','5 Starling Drive','1995-10-19','awalchr@ehow.com'),
