	 ('Gretna Codi','3657 Haas Place','2001-06-22','adorint@state.gov','Corn Flour, Starch','Corn flour is derived from the ground and desiccated seed of the maize plant. It is the second most produced and consumed flour after wheat flour. It is a good source of antioxidants, vitamins and minerals. It is rich in phytochemicals and also provides protection against several chronic diseases as well as reduces the risk of hemorrhoids and colorectal cancer.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',50,'2022-06-19',NULL,'created','Ailene Dorin','7 Hooker Point','1990-03-06','adorint@google.es'),
	 ('Othello Dimmick','23866 Stoughton Terrace','2001-04-12','mborleaseu@geocities.jp','HandMade Women Blue Printed Kurta with Palazzos','Blue printed kurta with palazzos Blue A-line calf length kurta, has a round neck, short sleeves, flared hem Blue solid palazzos, button closure','clothes',73,'2022-08-01',NULL,'in progress','Myrtle Borlease','27195 Pennsylvania Court','2000-04-27','mborleaseu@dailymail.co.uk'),
	 ('Ettie Weond','471 Farragut Road','2004-08-27','oboonv@live.com','Organic - Whole Wheat Atta/Godihittu','Organic Whole Wheat Attas are sent percent wheat grain atta with fiber and are recognized in the market for their normal ingredients. Whole grains or foods made from them contain all the essential parts and naturally-occurring nutrients of the entire grain seed in their original proportions. This definition means that 100% of the original kernel – all of the bran, germ, and endosperm – must be present to qualify as a whole grain. It develops the digestive system and consists of iron. Organic Whole Wheat Atta is the carefully select, cleaned, fresh and maintained one.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',82,'2022-06-24','2022-06-26','done','Onofredo Boon','2 Almo Center','1997-01-04','oboonv@phpbb.com'),
	 ('Roderigo Drewet','92688 Blue Bill Park Center','1999-07-16','agildroyw@google.ca','HandMade Men Blue Slim Fit Printed Casual Shirt','Blue printed casual shirt, has a spread collar, long sleeves, button placket,  curved hem, one patch pocket','clothes',73,'2022-10-23',NULL,'in progress','Allen Gildroy','421 Annamark Court','1992-08-17','agildroyw@pen.io'),
	 ('Jackie Spellesy','2100 Butternut Center','2001-08-14','cbaccusx@sfgate.com','Basmati Rice - Mogra, Broken/Tukda 5 Kg + Wheat Flour (Chakki Atta) 10 Kg','Basmati Rice - Mogra, Broken/Tukda: Sourced from the rice-bowl-states of Punjab, Haryana and Uttarakhand, it is processed in GMP plants using Swiss technology to ensure superior quality and nutrition value. The HandMade Mogra basmati rice leaves a lasting impression because of its aroma, flavour and fluffy texture.Wheat Flour (Chakki Atta): Atta is made from the choicest grains - heavy on the palm, golden amber in colour and hard in a bite. It is carefully ground using modern chakki grinding process for the perfect balance of colour, taste and nutrition which also ensures that BB Royal atta contains 0% Maida. The dough made from BB Royal Atta absorbs more water, hence rotis remain softer for longer.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',53,'2022-12-04',NULL,'in progress','Cecil Baccus','2945 Southridge Street','1993-07-25','cbaccusx@dedecms.com'),
	 ('Starlene Kerley','451 Harper Street','2002-10-06','eserrisy@shutterfly.com','HandMade Men Brown Leather Formal Slip-Ons','A pair of brown square-toed formal slip-on shoes, has elasticated gussets on both sidesLeather upper, has a textured detailCushioned footbedTextured TPR outsoleWarranty: 3 months against manufacturing defect onlyWarranty provided by the brand owner / manufacturer','clothes',60,'2022-11-19',NULL,'in progress','Ellswerth Serris','45 Annamark Parkway','1996-06-14','eserrisy@csmonitor.com'),
	 ('Martin Phipson','25563 Dennis Court','2002-10-01','mashdownz@irs.gov','Basmati Rice Mini Mogra, Broken/Tukda 5 Kg  + Wheat Flour (Chakki Atta) 5 Kg','Basmati Rice Mini Mogra, Broken/Tukda: HandMade Mini Mogra Basmati rice leaves a lasting impression because of its flavour and fluffy texture. 1401 and 1121 variety of raw rice ensures great quality and taste. Sourced from the Basmati-rice-bowl states of Punjab, Haryana and Uttarakhand, this rice is processed in GMP plants using Swiss technology to ensure superior quality and high nutritional value. With its small size, this rice is best suitable for daily dishes like dal chawal, khichdi and kheer.Wheat Flour (Chakki Atta):  Atta is made from the choicest grains - heavy on the palm, golden amber in colour and hard in bite. It is carefully ground using modern chakki - grinding process for the perfect balance of colour, taste and nutrition which also ensures that BB Royal atta contains 0% Maida. The dough made from BB Royal Atta absorbs more water, hence rotis remain softer for longer.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',24,'2022-05-27',NULL,'created','Margo Ashdown','21 Forest Terrace','2001-04-04','mashdownz@businessweek.com'),
	 ('Abran Whitelaw','43 Shoshone Park','1997-12-09','cbehr10@dailymotion.com','HandMade Men Blue Slim Fit Checked Casual Shirt','Blue checked casual shirt, has a spread collar, long sleeves, button placket,  curved hem, one pocket','clothes',27,'2022-09-13','2022-09-15','done','Corissa Behr','2125 Summer Ridge Hill','2003-03-04','cbehr10@friendfeed.com'),
	 ('Juliane Janiak','6 Doe Crossing Circle','1992-10-13','gstalf3b@examiner.com','Hapima Crispy Fry Mix','A Mix That Enables Consumers To Create Restaurant Style Fried Chicken At Home  ','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',47,'2022-05-17','2022-05-18','done','Guenna Stalf','04 Bultman Terrace','2001-04-30','gstalf3b@redcross.org'),
	 ('Kristal Coultas','9611 Cherokee Hill','2000-04-09','bpecht11@constantcontact.com','Organic - Rice Flour/Akki Hittu','Rice flour is obtained from thinly ground rice. It is minced from raw white rice and is used in making various tasty dishes. Rice flour acts as a healthy thickening agent in few refrigerated recipes, it gives the dishes smooth consistency. Rice flour is gluten free and a fine substitute for wheat flour. It is used to make sweets and rice noodles and also has an extensive use in baby food products. It is free from synthetic chemicals and pesticides.
