	 ('Glenn Challener','74 Killdeer Hill','2004-08-24','spickersail1c@about.com','HandMade Off-White & Blue Geometric 210TC Cotton 1 King Bedsheet with 2 Pillow Covers','Set content: 1 King bedsheet with 2 pillow coversQuality: FineThread count: 210Colour: Off-White and bluePattern: Geometric','clothes',2,'2022-12-12',NULL,'delivery','Sharai Pickersail','31 Springs Trail','1999-01-19','spickersail1c@irs.gov'),
	 ('Doloritas Helm','439 Linden Crossing','2004-07-04','amurkitt1d@dailymail.co.uk','Puttu Podi','Puttu is the favourite breakfast of kids and youngsters in Kerala. Puttu is also famous in Tamil Nadu. Basically, puttu is steamed cylinders of ground rice layered with grated coconut. The rice powder used for Puttu is different from all other varieties of rice batter which is used for traditional South Indian breakfast because of its coarse nature and drier texture. HandMade Puttu Powder is an ideal mix or pure rice, coarse ground to make puttu tasty. Steam passes through the thick cylinder due to the coarse nature of the ground rice and multiple layers of grated coconut. This also provides its own aroma and taste and tops up the sweetness.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',13,'2022-10-18','2022-10-20','done','Ad Murkitt','35772 Raven Road','1999-07-24','amurkitt1d@moonfruit.com'),
	 ('Ben McBrady','70 6th Lane','1997-04-18','sstocking1f@ustream.tv','Nature''s Super Foods - Ragi Flour/Ragi Hittu','Known for their numerous health benefits, Millets have been a part of the Indian food culture for thousands of years. Millets can be used to prepare a range of mouth-watering dishes.At HandMade, we value the goodness that comes from tradition. HandMade brings to you Superfoods to make your family Super Fit. HandMade Nature''s Superfoods have been expertly sourced, carefully processed and hygienically packed to ensure you the best of nutrition and taste. All these Superfoods come loaded with nutritional benefits - Rich in Dietary Fibre, Source of Protein, Naturally Gluten Free. Further, each Superfood offers additional nutritional benefits specific to the flour!','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',10,'2022-05-05',NULL,'in progress','Shalna Stocking','99317 Ronald Regan Junction','2002-06-18','sstocking1f@bigcartel.com'),
	 ('Winthrop Wollacott','9 School Pass','1992-06-25','jgorton1g@epa.gov','HandMade Plus Size Blue Solid Underwired Lightly Padded T-shirt Bra P5441','Blue solid medium-coverage T-shirt braLightly padded and underwired seamless cupsRegular straps and back closureBack style: RegularFeature: All Day Comfort','clothes',61,'2022-09-18',NULL,'created','Jaquelin Gorton','82 Jana Court','1999-08-29','jgorton1g@google.pl'),
	 ('Kendal Chatelet','111 Jackson Lane','2002-09-14','rdyers1h@yellowpages.com','Bajra Flour','Bajra flour is made from small round grains of black millet, also called bajra. The flour is greyish in colour and has a slightly nutty flavour. Since it is a heat-producing ingredient, it is commonly used in winters.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',86,'2022-05-31',NULL,'in progress','Raychel Dyers','72231 Nova Alley','1992-07-19','rdyers1h@exblog.jp'),
	 ('Dael Eagell','588 Duke Place','2004-05-27','rwooton1i@jimdo.com','HandMade Men Grey Melange Printed Round Neck T-shirt','Grey printed T-shirt, has round neck, long sleeves','clothes',79,'2022-09-02',NULL,'delivery','Robbi Wooton','4 Algoma Avenue','1994-06-26','rwooton1i@qq.com'),
	 ('Karney Brigg','92 Sage Junction','1997-06-27','skybbye1j@yahoo.co.jp','Ragi - Huri Hittu','Ragi Huri Hittu, Is One Of The Delicious Products Are Very Rich In Calcium, Fibre And Iron.These Ragi Items Are Prepared Under Natural Procedures Without Using Additives And Preservatives.  ','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',85,'2022-07-19','2022-07-20','done','Suzy Kybbye','665 Eastwood Avenue','1998-03-15','skybbye1j@live.com'),
	 ('Lodovico Wakefield','6 Charing Cross Center','1997-07-18','esharrem1k@omniture.com','HandMade Men White Printed Round Neck T-shirt','White and black printed T-shirt,has round neck,short sleeves','clothes',94,'2022-06-02',NULL,'in progress','Elset Sharrem','02578 Autumn Leaf Parkway','1991-10-04','esharrem1k@discovery.com'),
	 ('Dari Oselton','0 Westend Junction','1999-08-25','tbassingden1l@netvibes.com','Atta/Godihittu - Chakki Fresh','Is Pure Premium Quality Wholesome Atta Made Using Premium Sharbati Wheat Blend, Wheat Grains Sourced From The Bountiful Wheat Fields Of Madhya Pradesh And Rajasthan. The Grains Are Chakki-Ground In Traditional Fashion After Three Times Of Intensive Cleaning In A State-Of-The-Art  Plant With Latest Swiss Technology Equipment, Completely Automated Process System With Hygiene Handling And Packing Operations  ','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',71,'2022-05-08',NULL,'delivery','Tuesday Bassingden','17 Blue Bill Park Pass','1992-05-07','tbassingden1l@fotki.com'),
