	 ('Sena Coveley','3960 Dakota Plaza','2002-06-24','whartles1p@soup.io','Podi - Puttu','HandMade Puttu podi can be used to create soft, tasty Puttu with a pleasantly delicious smell. Care for yourself and your family to a tasty breakfast with immediate Puttu Podi.  ','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',9,'2022-10-17',NULL,'created','Will Hartles','1 Lien Parkway','2000-02-02','whartles1p@tuttocitta.it'),
