	 ('Emmey Vose','52 Little Fleur Junction','2000-02-24','bdudbridge1r@creativecommons.org','Rava - Samba Wheat','Rava is made of semolina which is a healthy option. It’s nutritious and can be easily digested. has a rich flavour and aroma and provides essential amino acids for complete protein. Used in a variety of soups, salads, sweets and savouries, Sooji Ravva is essential in every household. This rava can be directly used in cereals, puddings & sweet dishes like halwa and salty dishes such as dosa, idly, upma, uttapam and vada. It can also be used as a dietary supplement. It has been in the market for more than five decades. It offers various food products across a variety of categories.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',76,'2022-11-04',NULL,'created','Berkley Dudbridge','291 Blackbird Court','1995-05-18','bdudbridge1r@freewebs.com'),
	 ('Edgardo Gabey','912 Arkansas Crossing','1998-02-01','aokenden1s@tmall.com','HandMade Plus Size Red Solid Underwired Lightly Padded T-shirt Bra P5391','Red solid medium-coverage T-shirt bra Lightly Padded and Underwired seamless cups Regular straps and back closure Back style: Regular Feature: All Day Comfort','clothes',92,'2022-09-12',NULL,'delivery','Adrian Okenden','66 Truax Crossing','1998-04-29','aokenden1s@fastcompany.com'),
	 ('Vail Magnay','3 Briar Crest Crossing','1990-10-08','mtye1t@nationalgeographic.com','Rice Puttupodi','Puttu is a Kerala food at its best. white puttupodi will ensure that you relish the traditional breakfast of steamed puttu served with assorted dishes. This is a highly popular dish from Kerela and Sri Lanka.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',19,'2022-10-23',NULL,'in progress','Missie Tye','85 Leroy Park','1997-03-25','mtye1t@mediafire.com'),
	 ('Rozanne Carlens','83230 Reinke Road','2004-02-01','gtomlins1v@auda.org.au','Rice Powder','This is natural white rice flour, which can be used for making Ada, Vattayappam, Nayyappam, Unniyappam, roti, murukku, and nippittu. HandMade Rice Powder gives you the best of natural rice and the perfect formula to pamper your taste buds with delicacies.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',75,'2022-12-04',NULL,'created','Georgette Tomlins','77 Moland Point','1991-09-24','gtomlins1v@phoca.cz'),
	 ('Flss Annis','54381 Cody Hill','1994-05-04','lcayton1w@barnesandnoble.com','HandMade Women Multicoloured Printed Belt','Multicoloured printed beltReversible: NoStretchable: NoSecured with a tangWarranty: 1 monthWarranty provided by brand/manufacturer','clothes',67,'2022-05-04',NULL,'delivery','Lynna Cayton','22 8th Crossing','2004-03-04','lcayton1w@moonfruit.com'),
	 ('Rollins Smellie','5414 Westerfield Point','1994-10-03','emounch1x@army.mil','Ragi Flour/Ragi Hittu - Pesticide Free','This Whole Selected Ragi Floor Ragi Flour can be used to make healthy porridge and can also be used in the preparation of different yummy dishes like adai, dosa, puttu The high level of fibres in Ragi slows down the pace of digestion thereby helping in lowering blood sugar levels. It works as a natural relaxant and helps in relieving stress-related ailments like anxiety, hypertension, depression and headaches. It also helps in relieving insomnia and migraine.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',89,'2022-05-16',NULL,'in progress','Emile Mounch','3 Waubesa Terrace','2000-12-04','emounch1x@google.fr');
