	 ('Thane Sidnall','07537 Bowman Drive','1992-09-25','bropkins21@thetimes.co.uk','Roasted Rava','Rava or Sooji as it is called is a purified variety of wheat middlings is used primarily for preparing upma, pancakes, baby cereals, rava dosa and sweet dishes like kesari/ksheera. HandMade Rava/Sooji is also famous across India for the preparation of Halwas.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',70,'2022-10-05',NULL,'in progress','Beilul Ropkins','50 Jackson Park','1995-11-23','bropkins21@sina.com.cn'),
	 ('Katalin Narramore','85271 Fieldstone Crossing','2004-09-04','pposselt22@noaa.gov','HandMade Set of 3 Blue & Off-White Handpainted Kitchen Storage Jars with Lids','Type:  Set of 3 Blue & Off-White Handpainted Kitchen Storage Jars with LidsPattern: PrintedFinish: GlossyMaterial: Ceramic','clothes',64,'2022-05-20',NULL,'in progress','Philbert Posselt','76 Corscot Avenue','1998-12-11','pposselt22@netvibes.com'),
	 ('Freddi Glandon','2426 Kennedy Hill','1994-05-19','earch23@woothemes.com','Organic - Red Rice Flour/Akki Hittu','Red rice flour is the milled product from premium quality red raw rice and is a wholesome addition to your diet. The organic staple contains antioxidants, is a rich source of Vitamin B6, is rich in fibre, and helps in keeping high cholesterol, blood sugar levels, obesity, asthma, risk of heart disease in check. It is high in fibre and associated with a host of health benefits: Aids digestion. Heals stomach and mouth ulcers. Improves immunity and stamina. Strengthens muscles and nerves. Supplies instant energy to the body. Increases haemoglobin content. Good for diabetics since it is has a low Glycemic Index. You can use red rice flour to make a variety of dishes including bread, cakes, fresh pasta and so on.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',34,'2022-11-09','2022-11-11','done','Ernaline Arch','247 Mendota Place','2001-03-07','earch23@phoca.cz'),
	 ('Gordon Gartenfeld','58 Forest Run Court','2004-02-21','shacon24@bloglovin.com','HandMade Blue & Green Printed Wooden Open Dry Bin','Set content: 1 open dry binColour: Blue and greenPattern: Floral printShape: Rectangular','clothes',62,'2022-11-08',NULL,'created','Sarine Hacon','6 Reindahl Avenue','1997-10-21','shacon24@yandex.ru'),
	 ('Tam Cunnington','6 Londonderry Point','1996-05-18','lglavias25@edublogs.org','Podi - Chemba Puttu','HandMade Chemba Puttu Podi is a broad collection of exotic, traditional rice based breakfast items are especially well-liked in still modern houses. The quality of brown rice powder is used to create wonderfully healthful Chemba Puttu that''s a pleasure to spread on.  ','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',80,'2022-10-22',NULL,'in progress','Lavina Glavias','5 Prairieview Street','1993-02-20','lglavias25@chron.com'),
	 ('Genevieve Sawer','42 Summit Avenue','1995-12-06','amaleney26@epa.gov','HandMade Plus Size Black Lace Non-Wired Non Padded Everyday Bra P5482','Black lace full-coverage everyday braNon padded and non-wired cut and sew cupsRegular straps and back closureBack style: RegularFeature: Side Bone','clothes',99,'2022-11-09',NULL,'in progress','Amalia Maleney','7 Gulseth Crossing','1992-10-21','amaleney26@alexa.com'),
	 ('Hermione O''Scollee','24 Luster Terrace','1990-05-20','lluesley27@dell.com','6 Grain Khichdi Mix - Ready To Cook','With work consuming all our day and life getting increasingly hectic, one is often left with no time to cook something that is nutritious as well as delicious. Introducing HandMade’s Ready To Cook products that are a great source of nutrients and amazing in taste. HandMade Supergrain Mixes are made with Millets, also known as Nutri Cereals, as they provide wholesome nutritional goodness including micronutrients and dietary fibre, Nutri Cereals are known to have better nutritional benefits compared to commonly used staple grains and hence are a ''Powerhouse of Nutrients''. With the goodness of sulphur-rich amino acids, calcium, phosphorus, and magnesium, Ragi Dosa Mix goes through stringent quality specifications to provide you with the best quality and taste. The ragi dosa doesn''t need to be soaked overnight or ground. Containing no added preservatives and colours the dosa can be easily prepared in 3 easy steps and is perfect for breakfast or evening snacks. So, whenever you are in the mood to cook something quick and yummy, dive into the scrumptious taste of ragi dosa mix and enjoy!
