	 ('Andi Westmancoat','584 North Court','2001-05-19','cranderson2y@tripadvisor.com','HandMade Set Of 5 Handcrafted Ceramic Kulladhs','Set Of 5 Ceramic Kulladhs Pattern: PrintedFinish: GlossyMaterial: CeramicFeatures: Handcrafted','clothes',71,'2022-10-09',NULL,'delivery','Cathlene Randerson','0 Burning Wood Terrace','1990-08-12','cranderson2y@youtu.be'),
	 ('Mario Coppins','4 Schlimgen Lane','1992-09-18','mosgar2z@wiley.com','Chia Seeds Flour','Nutriwish seeks to help you achieve a healthy and active life that you wish to lead, by delivering nutrition suited to your needs. we deliver an eclectic range of nutritious superfoods from across the world to bring out the super you in you. Nutriwish 100% Chia Seeds Flour is a rich source of omega-3 fatty acids and package of minerals and vitamins. It is a tremendous plant-based source of protein and is a rich source of omega-3 essential fatty acids or good fats. Excellent source of both soluble and insoluble fibre, chia seeds exhibit a high antioxidant activity, which is associated with the polyphenolic compounds. It helps in weight management by suppressing hunger pangs.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',73,'2022-10-05',NULL,'in progress','Melodee Osgar','18508 Forest Run Circle','2003-10-14','mosgar2z@rambler.ru'),
