	 ('Gay Kolodziejski','6 Larry Point','1999-08-30','ogover31@wp.com','Fine Besan/Kadale Hittu - 100% Chana Dal','HandMade Fine Besan is all you need in the kitchen to enjoy an all-natural, authentic taste of 100% unpolished chana dal in all your favourite recipes. This besan lets you indulge in dishes like dhokla, kadhi, fafda, sev, and other namkeens without any compromise. HandMade Fine Besan undergoes a 5 step purity process to ensure that besan in every packet you buy is uniform and of premium quality. Karo Goodness ki Shuruaat!
