	 ('Emilee Dowsey','8708 Superior Road','1995-09-03','tdiamond35@linkedin.com','Gram Flour - Besan/Kadale Hittu','Gram flour or chickpea flour or besan is a pulse flour made from a variety of ground chickpea known as Bengal gram. This flour is used to make a variety of dishes.','Foodgrains, Oil & Masala',20,'2022-06-04',NULL,'created','Tiphany Diamond','304 Clove Road','1997-01-26','tdiamond35@bbc.co.uk'),
