	 ('Zacharie Klaaasen','697 Loeprich Road','1991-05-17','jpaine3x@ezinearticles.com','Bathing Soap','HandMade Soap is being used throughout the world for beneficial and softening the skin. This soap is finished from pure vegetable ingredients and contains Natural HandMadewood oil.  For Beauty tips, tricks & more visit https://bigbasket.blog/','Beauty & Hygiene',69,'2022-09-17',NULL,'delivery','Jereme Paine','691 Ronald Regan Lane','2000-01-08','jpaine3x@bbb.org'),
