	 ('Lowrance Leyband','718 Eastlawn Drive','2001-11-24','mzanetello41@twitpic.com','Antiseptic- Disinfectant Liquid 550 ml + Clinical Strength Hand Sanitizer 500 ml','Antiseptic - Disinfectant Liquid: HandMade Antiseptic Liquid protects you and your family from 100 illness-causing germs. It comes in a fresh pine fragrance. The topical antiseptic liquid sanitizes your home and helps maintain your personal hygiene.  It can be used to protect against infection from cuts and scratches, disinfect toys, and sanitize baby wear leaving everything clean and fresh. It can also be used as a household disinfectant and cleaner on surfaces or in laundry cleaning to kill germs. 
