	 ('Nissie Pitkin','95 Corry Pass','1992-06-25','atack4v@yellowpages.com','Hand Sanitiser - Germ Protection, Original','HandMade is one of the worlds most trusted antiseptic protection brand which give you 99. 99% protection against disease causing bacteria, germs and es. Their hand Sanitiser protects you from 100 illness causing germs and saves you the trouble of washing your hands with soap and water during emergencies.  | Germ protection in the classic HandMade fragrance. 
