	 ('Betty Hawe','3375 Algoma Court','1999-03-19','tburgill5d@twitter.com','Shower Gel - Aroma, Morning Tonic','HandMade Aroma Morning Tonic Shower Gel is an energizing body wash that awakens your senses with every wash. From enchanting the senses with its pleasant aroma to effective cleansing, HandMade shower gels are a perfect choiceIts uplifting lemony notes, from Tangerine essential oil and lemongrass extracts, provides you the essence of a blissful shower moment. Immerse yourself in the fragrance of this energizing HandMade body wash that helps to stimulate your mind and spirit in a blissful shower moment','Beauty & Hygiene',70,'2022-11-17','2022-11-20','done','Thaddus Burgill','23 Moland Center','1994-01-24','tburgill5d@nbcnews.com'),
