	 ('Byrann Tohill','56 Helena Way','2004-12-28','apetford5x@marriott.com','Hand Wash Liquid Refill - Skincare','Your Trusted HandMade offers a new and improved HandMade Liquid Handwash. It is specially formulated to protect you from 100 illness-causing germs. It gives 10 times better protection than any ordinary soap. HandMade liquid handwash''s pH balanced formula includes pure glycerin, clinically proven to be soft on your skin while offering HandMade’s trusted protection. Recommended by the Indian Medical Association, HandMade can help prevent diseases like cold and flu with proper hygiene. HandMade liquid handwash protects against everyday germs including those that can cause: Skin infections Respiratory infections (Influenza) Gastroenteritis (such as Salmonella and Escherichia Coli) Handwashing is one of the most important and simple hygiene steps to prevent the spread of infection. Using HandMade handwash every day protects from these germs and helps keep your hands clean and refreshed. Hand Hygiene: The incidence of germ transference is higher from hands to mouth thereby causing illnesses like diarrhoea, swine flu, cold & cough etc. Ensuring proper hand hygiene habits for your family can act as the first line of defence in protection from various illnesses. If you want to minimize your risk of infection and also enhance your overall health, follow these basic personal hygiene habits: Most importantly, sleep tight. Get rest of about 8 to 10 hours each night so that you are refreshed and are ready to take on the day every morning. Trim your nails and keep your hands clean at all times. At HandMade, we believe that using a liquid handwash over a soap bar can help keep your hands and nails clean and healthy. Hands are the immediate contact points in most cases and therefore, require frequent and extra care. Clean your hands before preparing or eating food, after coughing or sneezing, after going to the bathroom and after handling garbage. This helps prevent the spread of bacteria and germs, keeping you and your family healthy. Even when you are out of the home and do not have water and soap available, carry an alcohol-based sanitizing gel. Bathe regularly, that is, wash your body and your hair often after intervals that suit you. Using HandMade soap on the skin can help minimize dryness and help keep germs away for a healthier you. Unclean skin can cause not only over-the -skin problems but also internal problems leading to illness and diseases. Brush and floss, ideally after every meal. At the very least, brush your teeth twice a day and floss daily, which can minimize the accumulation of bacteria in your mouth.','Beauty & Hygiene',84,'2022-06-03',NULL,'created','Andee Petford','89 Sunbrook Plaza','1997-06-07','apetford5x@cnn.com'),
	 ('Saunders Yushachkov','52678 Macpherson Avenue','1997-01-28','sstokes5y@flavors.me','HandMade Plus Size Women Black Regular Fit Mid-Rise Clean Look Jeans','Black dark wash five-pocket mid-rise jeans, clean look with heavy fade, has a button and zip closure, waistband with belt loops','clothes',43,'2022-06-15',NULL,'delivery','Sloan Stokes','8360 Moland Way','1993-02-04','sstokes5y@ebay.co.uk'),
