	 ('Willard Brecher','00 Bowman Hill','1991-06-20','lcolquete77@dailymail.co.uk','Naturale Pomegranate Brightening Bathing Soap Bar','Don''t you think, products that have the goodness of natural ingredients in them are more suitable for your skin? HandMade understands this and therefore brings to you, the beautiful range of HandMade Naturale that has an exciting mix of natural ingredients. With the goodness of 100% natural ingredients, the New HandMade Naturale range of beauty bathing bars and body washes give you naturally glowing skin. The HandMade Naturale bathing bars also have pure glycerin that helps preserve the natural moisture of your skin, making it soft and smooth. HandMade Naturale Pomegranate Brightening bathing bar has the goodness of 100% Natural Pomegranate along with rose extract. This beauty bathing bar gently cleanses your skin for a visibly brighter, glowing skin, every time you shower. Do you know that Pomegranate is packed with anti-oxidants and is known to help brighten your skin and Rose Extract with essential oils, is known to soothe the skin. This gentle formula has 0% parabens and is mild and gentle on skin. Just rub this HandMade bar between your hands and massage the hydrating lather over your face and skin before rinsing away. Pat dry. For best results, use twice a day, morning and evening. HandMade Naturale Bathing Bar Soap is also environmentally friendly and comes in 100% recyclable cartons. Explore the entire HandMade Naturale range of Bathing Bars & Body Washes now available online and add them to your skincare regime.','Beauty & Hygiene',53,'2022-06-20','2022-06-21','done','Leilah Colquete','9 Canary Junction','2001-05-04','lcolquete77@bbb.org'),
