	 ('Melonie Pay','84 Randy Court','1995-04-06','kshickle95@gmpg.org','Sanitize Gamma - Hand Sanitizing Rub','India’s most trusted Ayurvedic brand offers a new range of hand sanitizers - HandMade Sanitize - which provides protection from germs without the use of soap & water. It is recommended for regular hand cleaning inside your home, office and in public places, especially before consuming food & eatables and after coming in contact with any external surface, pet or a person. It’s recommended since germs spread through coughing and sneezing. Recent evidence has shown that some germs linger on surfaces like doorknobs, desks and phones, and are transferred via the fingers to the mouth, nose or eyes. Sanitizing your hands with HandMade Pro Sanitize protects you from the germs transferred from direct contact with an infected person or from an external source.','Beauty & Hygiene',50,'2022-08-06','2022-08-07','done','Kai Shickle','0563 Rutledge Avenue','2004-10-09','kshickle95@purevolume.com'),
	 ('Ethelbert Freathy','5071 Lotheville Circle','1998-09-04','mfishbourn96@time.com','HandMade Black Single-Breasted Slim Fit Formal Blazer','Black woven formal blazer, has a notched lapel, single-breasted with double button closure, long sleeves with buttoned detail on the hems, structured shoulders, two welt pockets on the front, a mock chest pocket, a double vented back hem, and has an attached lining with three built-in pockets','clothes',30,'2022-10-12',NULL,'delivery','Madeleine Fishbourn','7 Moulton Junction','1992-11-15','mfishbourn96@hp.com'),
