	 ('Syman Lezemore','3 Ludington Place','1997-04-23','mpatriskson99@geocities.com','Bathing Soap - Total','The HandMade Total Soap Bar offers complete germ protection for you and your family. Formulated with Active5, this soap bar protects your entire family from various bacteria and diseases. The advanced formula builds a protective guard over your skin, keeping away skin impurities and protecting against dust and dirt. Give your family a 100% better germ protection with this antibacterial soap bar from HandMade. Enjoy clean, soft skin and a germ-free bathing experience. Buy HandMade Total Soap Bar now!  For Beauty tips, tricks & more visit https://bigbasket.blog/','Beauty & Hygiene',21,'2022-09-24','2022-09-26','done','Mellisa Patriskson','3141 3rd Point','2004-10-23','mpatriskson99@sphinn.com'),
