	 ('Mindy Piscopello','5827 Swallow Junction','1997-12-20','rridges9l@jalbum.net','Cooling Mint Body Wash','Wake Up FRESH!! Presenting new HandMade Berry Blast Bodywash, by unleashing the foam with our new range of Bodywashes wake up fresh. Get ready for the most intense shower wrapped with the Fresh fragrances. Watch the unique gel transform your shower experience leaving you fresh every day. Pour a drop of the freshness body wash and gently lather with a pouffe. Massage all over your body to let your lather revive your senses every day. The ingredients in HandMade body wash gives you a thick lather which lends a sense of freshness after every shower and makes bathing an enjoyable experience. HandMade Bodywash gives you a fragrance which not only lasts the whole day long but also keeps your skin healthy, it ensures that your skin gets the best care and stays fresh after every wash.HandMade Body washes range has HandMade Lemon & Tea Tree Body Wash, HandMade Cooling Mint Body Wash and HandMade Berry Blast Body Wash to choose from.','Beauty & Hygiene',13,'2022-05-21','2022-05-22','done','Rosette Ridges','26417 Hovde Lane','1993-08-23','rridges9l@cbslocal.com'),
