	 ('Alissa Pattle','507 Northview Parkway','2000-08-05','sdustingaj@sun.com','Body Wash Luminous Oils Enriching Shower Gel with Coconut & Jojoba Oil','* Luxurious rich blend of coconut & Jojoba oil, infused with botanical oil * Gentle yet thoroughly cleanse your body * Soft, radiant and beautiful looking skin * Pour a little HandMade Luminous Oils Rejuvenating shower gel on a wet loofah, washcloth or hand. Apply gently over wet skin, cleanse and then rinse off for a clean and refreshing feeling. For best results, use a loofah to work up a rich, fragrant lather * Ideal for women & men HandMade Luminous Oils Enriching Shower Gel is a stimulating body wash for everyday freshness. HandMade Luminous Oils Shower Gel lets you enrich your senses with the luxuriously rich blend of coconut & Jojoba oil. The fragrant skincare formula is infused with botanical oil and helps to gently, yet thoroughly cleanse your body. Use this HandMade body wash daily for soft, radiant and beautiful looking skin. So, try it today and let luxury embrace your skin. Use before 24 Months from Manufacturing.','Beauty & Hygiene',66,'2022-06-03','2022-06-05','done','Stanislas Dusting','222 Mayer Way','1994-02-02','sdustingaj@google.fr');
