	 ('Phylys Leyban','455 Sherman Avenue','1999-10-03','llethardye4@icio.us','HandMade German Silver and Gold Plating Jewellery Set','Gold-Plated and red antique necklace, has drawstring closureComes with a pair of gold plated earrings, has post and back closure','clothes',85,'2022-11-04',NULL,'delivery','Leonora Lethardy','59 Beilfuss Place','2003-03-19','llethardye4@unicef.org'),
