	 ('Serena Skivington','8391 Mcbride Lane','2001-08-06','dcoattsex@unicef.org','Cool Fresh Menthol - Germ Protection Handwash','HandMade, World’s number 1 selling germ protection soap, brings to you Superfast handwash for Superfast kids. Kids are always in a hurry, even when washing hands. That is why switch to Superfast HandMade handwash. With every wash, this Activ Silver Formula gives you germ protection in just 10 seconds. Protect your family every day with HandMade Handwash. We use our hands for multiple tasks through the day - causing hands to gather germs. Simple hand hygiene habits for your family can be the first line of defence in protection from various illness-causing germs. Washing hands with soap or handwash instead of washing hands with just plain water are recommended. This can help protect you and your family from ingesting infection-causing germs that are sitting on your hands. The HandMade Handwash range has Total 10, Cool Fresh, Nature, Mild care and Lemon Fresh variants to choose from. In case water is not available, carry the pocket-sized sanitizer from HandMade to keep germs at bay. Alcohol-based sanitizers from HandMade kills 99.99% germs without water. New refers to the new pack,  as per lab test on indicator organism, 10 secs refers to lathering time and washes away the germs.','Beauty & Hygiene',57,'2022-11-03','2022-11-06','done','Dannye Coatts','37070 Novick Avenue','2004-02-09','dcoattsex@who.int'),
