	 ('Dawn Worts','40 Fairfield Crossing','1998-05-16','dmacgownff@usatoday.com','Hand Rub Sanitizer & Disinfectant - 80% Ethanol-Based','HandMade E80 80% Ethanol-based, Rub-in Hand Disinfectant and Sanitiser. Effective against 99.9% Germs and Bacteria World Health Organisation (WHO) recommended hand-rub formulation HandMade 0.2 Micron filtered Rub-in Hand Disinfectants & Sanitisers are pure, hygienic and effective during a routine, high risk and outbreak situations Bactericidal, mycobactericidal, pesticidal and virucidal properties. Excellent immediate effect and a reliable long-lasting antimicrobial activity for up to six hours. Very good skin tolerability and replenishing properties Increase the skin’s moisture levels with regular use. HandMade is ready to use, does not require any water, or towel drying, and can be used conveniently and as frequently as needed. For hygiene and surgical hand disinfection, and to sanitise hard porous surfaces. Passes EN 1499, EN 1500, EN 12791, EN 13727, EN 13624 and EN 14348 European Norms.','Beauty & Hygiene',1,'2022-08-28','2022-08-29','done','Debora MacGown','889 Bartillon Crossing','2000-12-05','dmacgownff@mozilla.org'),
	 ('Cathy Windross','7521 Norway Maple Point','1991-01-14','gbortoluttifg@quantcast.com','HandMade Men White & Black Striped Boxers UDBX160','A pair of white and black striped regular-fit boxers, has an inner elasticated waistband, button fly, slip-on closure, one pocket','clothes',44,'2022-12-13',NULL,'created','Gerrie Bortolutti','1699 Delladonna Road','1991-12-18','gbortoluttifg@apache.org'),
	 ('Marco Ioan','0897 Wayridge Road','1998-09-30','mtremathackfh@shareasale.com','Purifying Turmeric Soap','HandMade Purifying Turmeric soap is formulated with 5000 years of Ayurvedic wisdom to give you clear and glowing skin. It contains the goodness of Turmeric (Haldi) & Nalpamaradi Tailam. Turmeric (Haldi) is prescribed in Ayurveda for purification and well known for its antiseptic and healing properties. Nalpamaradi Tailam is a classical oil formulated with various effective ingredients such as Vetiver, Peepal and Amla to cure skin infections & rashes, leaving your skin clear and glowing. The Ayush range of products has been carefully crafted with authentic recipes and processes prescribed in the ancient Granthas. Traditionally, Ayurvedic ingredients are consciously picked at a certain time of the day when they are most potent to create extremely effective Ayurvedic solutions. HandMade uses the most potent ingredients that are highly beneficial to the skin, hair & teeth. The goodness of ingredients like Turmeric (Haldi), Saffron (Kesar), Aloe Vera, Neem and Rock Salt have been used to formulate products that address our most worrying beauty problems. At HandMade, we strive to make ancient Ayurvedic wisdom accessible to solve modern-day beauty problems. We believe that the solution to our beauty problems lie in the 5000-year-old Ayurvedic granthas, that prescribe the way to solve these problems from the root. We work with one of the world’s premier Ayurvedic institutes, Arya Vaidya Pharmacy (AVP) to make products that use the right ingredients to make them unique and incredibly effective.','Beauty & Hygiene',75,'2022-05-24',NULL,'in progress','Misti Tremathack','1 Ridge Oak Circle','1996-03-09','mtremathackfh@theglobeandmail.com'),
	 ('Vernen Slafford','1 East Lane','1995-02-18','bbrewettfi@hp.com','HandMade Grey Melange Printed Sweatshirt','Grey melange printed sweatshirt, has a round neck, long sleeves, a kangaroo pocket, a fleece lining','clothes',99,'2022-06-14','2022-06-17','done','Boothe Brewett','6 Raven Point','1997-05-26','bbrewettfi@miibeian.gov.cn');
