	 ('Aubry Cosgrave','56 Warrior Circle','2004-05-06','amcgilvarygb@vk.com','Handwash Refil Pack','HandMadeHandwash with the goodness of Ayurveda is specially formulated with natural essential oils for effective germ protection for your hands. It effectively removes germs from your hand, leaving them clean and healthy. It''s pure, natural care you can trust.','Beauty & Hygiene',10,'2022-10-16',NULL,'created','Addie McGilvary','0 Crownhardt Street','2003-05-11','amcgilvarygb@hp.com'),
