	 ('Franciskus Maddison','26613 Glacier Hill Pass','1996-03-27','lconklinggd@discuz.net','Creme Care Soap - For Hands & Body','HandMade soaps offer reliable cleansing abilities with the caring qualities you expect from HandMade. Natural care substances support your skin in keeping its moisture, day by day. With HandMade cream soap, enriched with valuable almond oil, mild skin ingredients and vitamin f your skin gets smooth and gentle care and is protected from drying out.For Beauty tips, tricks & more visit https://bigbasket.blog/','Beauty & Hygiene',54,'2022-05-05',NULL,'in progress','Lizabeth Conkling','82 Thierer Park','2004-11-28','lconklinggd@pcworld.com'),
