	 ('Derick Christon','4314 Stang Alley','2003-01-04','mlawteygf@ning.com','Body Wash Gel - Waterlily & Oil Shower','Give your skin refreshing care with HandMade waterlily and oil shower gel. Enriched with care oil pearls that moisturise your skin, making it soft and supple. Let this fresh shower gel envelop your skin with a silky soft foam, while its invigorating scent of waterlily flowers stimulates your senses.','Beauty & Hygiene',37,'2022-08-26','2022-08-28','done','Mame Lawtey','19 Comanche Road','2001-01-18','mlawteygf@elpais.com'),
	 ('Charisse Patridge','94387 International Terrace','2003-06-14','jhulstromgg@msn.com','HandMade Plus Size Fuchsia Pink Lace Underwired Lightly Padded Plunge Bra P5351','Fuchsia pink lace medium-coverage Plunge braLightly Padded and Underwired cut and sew cupsRegular straps and back closureBack style: RegularFeature: All Day Comfort','clothes',49,'2022-10-08','2022-10-11','done','Jeana Hulstrom','7 Daystar Lane','1998-05-14','jhulstromgg@mapy.cz'),
	 ('Buddie Mortlock','192 West Road','1994-11-23','nwarwickergh@cpanel.net','Neem Tulsi & Aloe Vera Soap','HandMadeis a brand that has consistently stood by its promise of honesty and safety for the last 89 years and continues to do so. HandMadeharnesses the best of nature to provide safety and protection to your skin and that’s why it has stood the test of time as a component of the wisdom mothers pass on to their children to keep them safe. Now your favourite HandMadeis available in a pack of 8. It harnesses one of nature’s most potent protectors with 100 per cent pure neem oil and complements it with two of nature’s most effective caregivers - Tulsi and Aloe vera to bring together the best solution to fight your skins battles against dust, sweat and pollution. It does not merely cleanse your skin, it purifies it. HandMadepromises you a bath that will evoke the best of nature. Go safe outside with the best ever HandMadeskin protection. Go safe outside with the best ever HandMadefragrance. HandMadeaims to be your choice of a companion as you get ready to step out to take on the challenges of the world. So, what are you waiting for? Try the best ever HandMadeSoap and Go Safe Outside.','Beauty & Hygiene',10,'2022-05-15',NULL,'created','Nicola Warwicker','05225 Bluejay Park','1998-03-25','nwarwickergh@irs.gov'),
	 ('Ainslie Cinnamond','134 Schlimgen Plaza','1990-09-11','dessongi@storify.com','HandMade Men White Printed Polo Collar T-shirt','White printed T-shirt, has polo collar, short sleeves','clothes',14,'2022-05-16','2022-05-18','done','Daron Esson','65177 Lukken Alley','1993-02-16','dessongi@ftc.gov'),
	 ('Dottie Roach','228 Eliot Road','1999-02-15','pmawnegz@studiopress.com','Body Cleanser - Saundarya Sandal','For healthy & fair skin. Made from natural oil cleanser base, sandal wood oil extract of aloe vera which cleanses gently and keeps your skin glorified & soft, forever young and beautiful. Useful in nourishing, rejuvenating & glorifying the skin.  For Beauty tips, tricks & more visit https://bigbasket.blog/','Beauty & Hygiene',50,'2022-09-26',NULL,'created','Peadar Mawne','79 Green Ridge Street','1998-04-20','pmawnegz@apple.com'),
	 ('Binky Burtenshaw','55 Anthes Street','1991-04-25','rtipplegj@constantcontact.com','Air & Surface Disinfectant Spray','ZM Labs Surface & Air Disinfectant Spray is just what your home needs. It instantly kills 99.9% of bacteria. ZM Labs Surface & Air Disinfectant Spray disinfects not just air but also hard and soft surfaces in your house. It comes in an easy spray can which makes it convenient to use. Ethanol content is 70% and our special formulation makes it safe on skin. ZM Labs Surface & Air Disinfectant Spray is the best way to keep your surfaces disinfected.','Beauty & Hygiene',43,'2022-11-02',NULL,'delivery','Rinaldo Tipple','640 Amoth Hill','2003-05-01','rtipplegj@yellowbook.com'),
