	 ('Noellyn Hutt','519 Eastwood Hill','1993-01-15','nrossbrookekp@google.com','Sports Eucalyptus Shower Gel','Inaturs shower gels come in transparent gel form, are 100% soap-free and contain natural skin conditioners, essential oils, and extracts. Sports Shower Gel is a high-performance product that leaves your mind and body - active and fresh at the start of the day and also relaxes you after a tiring physical activity or sports.It is enriched with:Rosemary - has therapeutic properties, rehydrates and tones the skinTriclosan - an anti-bacterial agentEucalyptus - has healing properties, relieves you of muscle pain owing to its anti-inflammatory properties and is also a stimulant.','Beauty & Hygiene',30,'2022-11-15',NULL,'delivery','Norbert Rossbrooke','397 Bluestem Plaza','1993-10-22','nrossbrookekp@imageshack.us'),
