	 ('Birgit Matys','196 Roth Alley','1991-06-02','kvellalf@multiply.com','Lavender Luxury Shower Gel','This Luxurious foaming soap-free French Lavender Luxury Shower Gel with Vitamin E that gently cleanses and nourishes your skin. Feel the enchanting continental notes of French Lavender blended with Rosemary caress your body. Aloe Vera and Glycerine heal, soothe and hydrate your skin to retain moisture after a bath.','Beauty & Hygiene',76,'2022-07-06',NULL,'in progress','Karissa Vella','885 Quincy Crossing','1990-08-27','kvellalf@dot.gov'),
