	 ('Jacob Lenden','423 Del Mar Crossing','1997-08-03','abutteryml@blogspot.com','Almond Body Wash Soap','The HandMade''s Almond Body Wash is an Ayurvedic bathing bar which helps in cleansing and nourishing your skin. It is formulated with the natural ingredients such as Almond, Haldi and Brahmi. It moisturises your skin and makes it soft and smooth. It is suitable for all skin types and can be safely used on daily basis. This soap gently wash away body impurities making it smooth.','Beauty & Hygiene',4,'2022-07-25','2022-07-26','done','Ashton Buttery','396 Pawling Hill','1997-05-21','abutteryml@boston.com'),
	 ('Kirstin Duval','56 Oak Valley Circle','1992-11-27','cgrevemm@narod.ru','Blue Solid Pullover','Keep yourself warm and look smart donning this grey sweater from HandMade, featuring horizontal pinstripes. With full sleeves and knitted texture, this sweater is a great pick for mild winters. Team it with washed denims and sneakers. Contrast hem, cuffs and neck Knitted Horizontal pinstripes','clothes',95,'2022-06-13','2022-06-16','done','Caryl Greve','246 Almo Hill','1992-11-05','cgrevemm@reuters.com'),
