	 ('Roxana Cashley','0 Fordem Avenue','2001-04-21','gmaciejewskimp@netvibes.com','Sandal Body Wash Soap','The HandMade''s Sandal Body Wash is an Ayurvedic bathing bar which helps in gently cleaning your skin by removing dirt and impurities. This soap nourishes and moisturizes dry skin and makes it soft and smooth. It is useful in reducing pigmentation and spots. It is formulated with natural ingredients which is suitable for all skin types. This soap gently wash away body impurities making it smooth.','Beauty & Hygiene',79,'2022-10-01',NULL,'in progress','Gerta Maciejewski','6634 Eastlawn Park','2003-08-13','gmaciejewskimp@wsj.com'),
