	 ('Ward Vynall','0526 Southridge Pass','2002-07-05','hvaenmt@cafepress.com','Natural Green Tea Body Scrub','Natural Green Tea Body Scrub by HandMade. gently exfoliates, nourishes and smoothens the skin. The tub is loaded with the goodness of Green Tea, Black Sand, 5 plant AHAs and Vitamin C. It helps protect the skin with anti-oxidant rich Green Tea while Apricot Seed powder gently exfoliates without aggravating the skin with its perfectly sized particles. Black Sand and 5 plant AHAs remove dirt, dust and excess oil while Vitamin C stimulates collagen synthesis and protects the skin from damage caused by pollution and UV rays.','Beauty & Hygiene',53,'2022-08-19',NULL,'created','Hansiain Vaen','3393 Sunfield Pass','1990-12-16','hvaenmt@google.co.uk'),
