	 ('Kitti Sprigg','37 Fisk Avenue','1999-07-02','vmandynt@aol.com','Mandarin Citrus Handmade Soap','It has a refreshing zesty fragrance. Did you know that during the Chinese new year, Mandarin oranges and tangerines are considered traditional symbols of abundance and good fortune nyassa mandarin citrus is an active base soap? The active base is an exclusive and unique blend of six pure and natural carrier oils, essential oils and extracts that go into every nyassa handmade soap, namely aloe vera extract, grape seed extract, honey, cold pressed sweet almond oil, cold pressed wheat germ oil and Vitamin E Acetate. These ingredients work best as moisturisers, healers and soothing agents. HandMade''s zesty Mandarin citrus soap also contains two additional ingredients such as extracts of orange peel and lemon peel which helps to tighten the skin and protect from the body from tissue damage.','Beauty & Hygiene',75,'2022-05-25',NULL,'created','Vanni Mandy','934 Mitchell Trail','1998-02-09','vmandynt@go.com'),
	 ('Kaylyn Briscoe','26394 Waubesa Trail','2001-07-03','dmosbynu@dell.com','HandMade Set of 4 Turquoise Blue & Pink Printed Table Placemats','Set content: 4 table mats Shape: Rectangle Colour: Turquoise-blue and pink Pattern: Printed Suitable For: 4 seater table Material: Cotton ','clothes',43,'2022-12-07',NULL,'delivery','Demetris Mosby','55927 Service Hill','2002-11-24','dmosbynu@geocities.com'),
