	 ('Eddie Seabridge','43 Doe Crossing Alley','2001-08-19','jpeteraoh@usa.gov','Cold Processed Anti Tan Tomato Handmade Soap For Skin Brightening','100% pure, natural, vegan, cold-pressed and SLS free HandMade Juicy Red Tomato Soap, a handmade, hand-cut, natural oil-based soap. It is made from Fresh tomatoes, Beetroots, oils of Olive, Coconut, Castor and Palm with Vitamin E. This unique soap formulation uses the goodness of Vitamins A, B & E in tomatoes to lighten and brighten your skin while pure beetroot extract fades tan lines. Give your skin an antioxidant boost with the tangy aroma and abundant lather that protects and heals your skin from within. This soap is SLS free.','Beauty & Hygiene',40,'2022-09-25',NULL,'in progress','Janene Petera','4 Melrose Parkway','1999-01-07','jpeteraoh@thetimes.co.uk'),
