	 ('Xymenes Ropartz','68116 Corben Pass','1997-07-04','bretallackol@nps.gov','Loofah/Sponge Scrubber/Body Bath - Hangable, Dual Side, Brown, BH-061D BRN','This brown loofah/scrubber for hard to reach body parts. It is perfect for cleaning back, neck, feet etc. Just hold the loofah from the ends and gently scrub your body. It improves your skin''s blood circulation and eliminates the dead skin cells. The loofah is composed of cloth fibres that exfoliate the skin, resulting in the smooth and glowing skin.','Beauty & Hygiene',93,'2022-09-25',NULL,'delivery','Bear Retallack','32238 Petterle Street','2001-03-04','bretallackol@people.com.cn'),
