	 ('Waylen Daid','598 Harper Avenue','2002-03-20','theasleyon@disqus.com','Cold Processed Reetha Coconut Milk Hair Cleansing Bar - Anti Dandruff, Anti Hairfall','100% pure, natural, vegan and cold-pressed HandMade Reetha Coconut Milk Shampoo Bar Soap is a handmade hand-cut natural oil-based soap. This unique soap bar ensures that your hair shines all day long. Pure Lemon Oil is rich in Vitamin A and C and keeps your scalp healthy. Coconut milk rich in anti-microbial properties conditions the scalp while pure Reetha powder controls hair fall and restores the damage. Our unique soap formulation has a sweet aroma forms large bubbles and cleanses dirt, removes dandruff to make your hair soft and shiny.','Beauty & Hygiene',42,'2022-08-11',NULL,'delivery','Tammara Heasley','97 Elka Center','1994-05-13','theasleyon@prweb.com'),
	 ('Alec Foxworthy','6382 Claremont Lane','2002-03-15','mhelsdonoo@163.com','HandMade Plus Size Navy Blue Lace Underwired Non Padded Everyday Bra P5632','Navy Blue lace full-coverage everyday braNon padded and underwired cut and sew cupsRegular straps and back closureBack style: RegularFeature: Side Bone','clothes',84,'2022-06-15','2022-06-16','done','Mikaela Helsdon','104 Loftsgordon Alley','1997-01-02','mhelsdonoo@free.fr'),
	 ('Niel Paniman','32897 Fisk Pass','1993-06-12','jpitceathlypd@yale.edu','Nomarks - Antimarks Soap For Oily Skin','New HandMade nomarks soap helps remove excess oil, deep-rooted dirt and provides relief from sunburn, blemishes and acne or pimple problems. It is a natural antiseptic which provides deep pore cleansing. Its key ingredient neem is a miraculous herb which is medicinal in nature and has potent antibacterial and powerful healing properties. Neem effectively prevents and treats itching, rashes, acne and other skin ailments.','Beauty & Hygiene',93,'2022-10-11',NULL,'in progress','Jacki Pitceathly','1 Vidon Parkway','2003-05-05','jpitceathlypd@nih.gov'),
	 ('Vivia McCulloch','6481 Harper Trail','2002-09-05','cdoeop@cdbaby.com','Basil Body Wash & Scrub','The HandMade''s Basil Body Wash and Scrub is an Ayurvedic bathing bar which helps in cleaning your skin. This soap helps in removing dirt, impurities and pollutants from skin effectively. It is free from harmful chemicals which makes your skin soft and smooth. The soap is useful in healing skin related ailments such as acne and blackheads. It is formulated with natural ingredients which is suitable for all skin types. This soap gently wash away body impurities making it smooth.','Beauty & Hygiene',1,'2022-07-11',NULL,'delivery','Chrissy Doe','35 Kipling Way','2002-02-27','cdoeop@woothemes.com');
