	 ('Emiline Sperry','6 Forest Dale Alley','2001-11-19','tbillingsor@dailymotion.com','Emery Boards (MP-15)','Medium fine emery boards are the perfect all rounder. Use their medium side for shaking and the fine side to smooth the edge of the nail to a flawless finish  For Beauty tips, tricks & more visitÃ‚Â https://bigbasket.blog/','Beauty & Hygiene',57,'2022-07-09',NULL,'delivery','Trisha Billings','70558 John Wall Terrace','1993-10-22','tbillingsor@ebay.com'),
	 ('Heath Godden','48 Lien Street','2004-03-02','mgrubyos@blogs.com','HandMade Rust Red & Yellow Art Silk Woven Design Kanjeevaram Saree','Design Detail:Rust red and yellow woven design saree, has a zari borderBlouse PieceThe model is wearing a blouse from our stylists collection, see the image for a mock-up of what the actual blouse would look likeOrigin:Kanjeevaram sarees are made in the Kanchipuram region in Tamil Nadu. The fabric bears the images of all the scriptures embossed on the walls of the temples of the Kanchipuram village.Fabric:Art silk is manufactured by synthetic fibres like rayon. It''s light in weight and is soft on the skin for comfort in summers.','clothes',50,'2022-05-06','2022-05-09','done','Marjorie Gruby','468 Eastwood Junction','1998-10-08','mgrubyos@alibaba.com'),
	 ('Rockwell Goose','76835 Namekagon Pass','1997-03-02','lmaddrellot@dailymotion.com','Rose & Lychee Soap','HandMade''s distinctive combination of rose and lychee fragrance inspired us to create an entire range of skincare products. A playful charm with a whole dose of tender care come together to add the perfect dash of character to this blend of fruity and floral fragrance. The HandMade Rose and Lychee handmade soap are created to pamper your skin with the wholesome goodness of Rose petal extract and Lychee extract. The pure play of aroma with the goodness of natural ingredients create this bath soap to pamper your skin. Rose petal extracts moisturise your skin while proving beneficial for skin toning. It also soothes sensitive skin. The pure Lychee extracts are an excellent source of Vitamin C and it also helps reduce facial lines.','Beauty & Hygiene',87,'2022-12-14',NULL,'in progress','Leyla Maddrell','57 South Terrace','1995-04-22','lmaddrellot@hatena.ne.jp'),
	 ('Bastian Firebrace','3216 Lotheville Trail','2004-11-14','jlowlessou@mail.ru','HandMade Men Black Solid Comfort Leather Sandals','A pair of black solidComfort SandalsLeather upper materialSole material: PUCushioned footbedPatterned synthetic outsoleWarranty: 3 monthsWarranty provided by brand/manufacturer','clothes',77,'2022-07-14',NULL,'delivery','Jacky Lowless','183 Chive Way','2003-03-12','jlowlessou@xinhuanet.com'),
	 ('Cody Garriock','555 Forest Dale Park','1991-06-22','wchidleyov@smugmug.com','Shea Butter Soap','It has a unique and sophisticated fragrance of Honey and saffron. Shea Butter is a luxurious active base butter soap from HandMade. ActiveBase is an exclusive and unique blend of six pure and natural carrier oils, essential oils and extracts that go into every HandMade handmade soap, namely aloe vera Extract, grape seed extract, honey, cold pressed sweet almond oil, cold pressed wheatgerm oil and Vitamin E Acetate. These ingredients work best as moisturisers, healers and soothing agents. Shea butter is a fantastic moisturiser, great for people with ageing skin. The butter contains a natural sun protectant and is high in Vitamin A and Vitamin E. HandMade''s luxurious shea butter soap contains two nutritious ingredients such as saffron and honey that helps to keep skin healthy and glowing. Saffron, perhaps the most expensive herb on earth, is proven to be a natural way to formulate radiant and glowing blemish free skin. Honey is a natural antioxidant that improves skin tone and prevents cell damages. Honey is also known to have some antimicrobial properties','Beauty & Hygiene',30,'2022-09-07',NULL,'in progress','Waverley Chidley','66572 Sutteridge Center','1999-01-25','wchidleyov@addthis.com'),
	 ('Granville Walles','9 Porter Place','2001-05-08','lhaileyow@mayoclinic.com','HandMade Men Black & Grey Standard Regular Fit Striped Casual Shirt','Black and grey striped casual shirt, has a mandarin collar, long sleeves, button placket, and curved hem','clothes',23,'2022-11-29',NULL,'delivery','Leif Hailey','637 Shoshone Trail','1991-08-04','lhaileyow@google.ca'),
	 ('Malina Wickman','905 Hooker Center','2002-09-27','onesterovox@aboutads.info','Glow Vanilla Lavender Body Polisher','The aromatic gel of pure herbs and essential oils for daily body cleansing in the shower uses exfoliating fine crystals which polish the skin, leaving it incredibly smooth & buffed. Lavender and honey are the powerhouses for providing a radiant and flawless complexion.','Beauty & Hygiene',87,'2022-07-13','2022-07-16','done','Osborn Nesterov','60 Nancy Court','1995-05-17','onesterovox@eventbrite.com'),
	 ('Des Ebunoluwa','40 Anniversary Junction','1994-04-09','mbucktharpoy@bbb.org','HandMade Women Blue Adora Skinny Fit Mid-Rise Slash Knee Stretchable Ankle Jeans','Blue medium wash 5-pocket mid-rise jeans, mildly distressed and slashed at one knee, heavy fade, has a button and zip closure, and waistband with belt loops','clothes',39,'2022-11-14','2022-11-16','done','Mia Bucktharp','1 Clove Way','1994-08-17','mbucktharpoy@cornell.edu'),
	 ('Florina Cleyburn','28 Anderson Center','1998-12-11','dalelsandrovichoz@si.edu','Pure Tea Tree Glycerin Soap - Cold-Processed, 100% Natural & Organic','Tea Tree Oil is regarded as one of the strongest natural antiseptics known to man. Because of its ability to inhibit and kill the growth of bacteria, fungi & germs, it makes a great medicinal soap for cuts & scrapes as well as a multi-purpose antibacterial and facial soap for everyday use. All you smell is the invigorating, minty smell of tea tree oil. Glycerin has humectants properties, attracting moisture to your skin making it softer & smoother, one of the reasons that our soaps are so beautiful on the skin. This soap does not use any animal product like milk or honey i. e. it is completely vegan and is SLS free.','Beauty & Hygiene',50,'2022-10-13','2022-10-14','done','Dael Alelsandrovich','93782 Loftsgordon Street','1999-02-14','dalelsandrovichoz@liveinternet.ru');
