	 ('Dorey Castrillo','700 Declaration Terrace','1997-11-18','pwernyp1@npr.org','Pure Orange Glycerin Soap With Coconut Oil - Cold Processed, 100% Natural & Organic','Every day your skin comes in contact with dirt, pollution, wind, sun and sweat. In spite of these setbacks, you can still have the softest, gentlest skin. Natural nutrients gently and effectively lighten dark spots for a more youthful and even-toned radiant skin. The rich lather rinses completely leaving no residue, while orange peel powder deep cleanses to remove dirt, bacteria, and oil and exfoliates dead skin cells for blemish-free dear skin, Works wonders on troubled teenage and oily skin. Glycerine has humectants properties, attracting moisture to your skin making it softer and smoother, one of the reasons that these soaps are so beautiful on the skin. This soap does not use any animal product like milk or honey. This product is SLS free.','Beauty & Hygiene',56,'2022-08-02','2022-08-04','done','Padget Werny','266 Westend Court','2002-03-19','pwernyp1@blinklist.com'),
	 ('Ulberto Duffrie','0 Sommers Way','1992-04-09','pcloneyp2@histats.com','HandMade Boys Navy Blue Slim Fit Printed Formal Trousers','Navy blue printed mid-rise formal trousers, button closure, zip fly and 5 pockets','clothes',62,'2022-09-12',NULL,'created','Pascale Cloney','6 Bellgrove Road','1995-07-16','pcloneyp2@livejournal.com'),
	 ('Michelle McCuis','260 Northridge Crossing','1992-09-14','akubachp3@unesco.org','Himalayan Pink Bath Salt','Himalayan pink salt is mined in the Khewra Salt Mines, the second largest salt mine in the world, located in Khewra, Punjab, Pakistan, about 300 km from the Himalayas. Himalayan Pink Salt is a pure, hand-mined salt that is derived from ancient sea salt deposits, and it is believed to be the purest form of salt available. The high mineral crystals range in colour from sheer white, varying shades of pink, to deep reds, the result of high mineral and iron content. HandMade Himalayan Pink Salt is the best way to take care of your skin during your bath. Himalayan Pink Salts contain more than 84 minerals and trace elements like calcium, copper, magnesium, potassium and iron that are all good for your skin and body. Regular use of Himalayan pink salt provides proper nutrient absorption, eliminates toxins, normalizes blood pressure, increases circulation, assists with relief from arthritis, skin rashes, flu and fever symptoms.','Beauty & Hygiene',60,'2022-12-31',NULL,'in progress','Amelina Kubach','9369 Mendota Drive','1993-03-15','akubachp3@last.fm'),
	 ('Elinor Bayston','4 Pine View Center','2004-02-18','nmoynep4@moonfruit.com','HandMade Rose Gold-Toned Contemporary Cufflinks','A pair of rose gold-toned contemporary textured cufflinksComes in a signature HandMade case','clothes',2,'2022-05-30',NULL,'in progress','Nicolle Moyne','7452 Macpherson Place','1990-05-01','nmoynep4@rediff.com'),
	 ('Perle Bristoe','7065 Dennis Center','2000-07-26','vrymillp5@telegraph.co.uk','Sandal Saffron Bath Salt','HandMade Natural Handmade Bath Salts have been developed to mimic the properties of natural mineral baths or hot springs. The best way to refresh you after a long tiring day is to soak yourself in them. So simply allow the salts to swirl around gently as you take a deep breath, lie back and unwind in your own personal bath. Simply adding the bath salt to your bath water has several benefits.Tip: Following a regular skin care regime can help you achieve flawless skin. For more tips on skin care, visit bigbasket lifestyle blog, ','Beauty & Hygiene',92,'2022-06-06','2022-06-07','done','Vincent Rymill','67454 Randy Hill','1997-05-10','vrymillp5@time.com'),
	 ('Grady Bosomworth','1 Stuart Hill','1997-11-23','bwitheyp6@nifty.com','Extreme Night Edt 70Ml','	A perfect pick for bold and daring urban man is this ''Extreme Night'' EDT from HandMade that gives a refreshing oriental scent. The top note of this EDT comprises bergamot, black pepper and nutmeg. The heart note comprises cypress, lily and clary sage that exude a pungent yet fresh scent, while the base note comprises a perfect harmony of musk, cedar, vanilla, sandalwood, tonka beans and orris. The net weight of this EDT is 70ml. ','clothes',61,'2022-10-09','2022-10-12','done','Brynna Withey','72895 Doe Crossing Lane','1996-03-09','bwitheyp6@oakley.com'),
	 ('Cheri Volant','7359 Forest Dale Parkway','2002-02-24','gnapperp7@theguardian.com','Loofah/Sponge Scrubber/Body Bath  - Hangable, Grey, BH-005 GRY','Have a refreshing bath experience with this loofah. It improves the circulation of your skin and eliminates the dead skin cells. The loofah sponge is composed of plastic mesh fibres that exfoliate the skin, resulting in the smooth and glowing skin.','Beauty & Hygiene',83,'2022-09-12',NULL,'in progress','Goldina Napper','592 Nova Parkway','2004-11-08','gnapperp7@hatena.ne.jp'),
	 ('Milzie Davidovic','415 Eagan Center','2003-11-18','ctidderp8@imageshack.us','HandMade Gold-Toned & Green Solid Handcrafted Table Lamp with Shade','Type: Handcrafted Table Lamp with ShadeColour: Gold-Toned and greenPattern: SolidShape: FrustumShade material: FabricBase material: AluminiumBulb Holder Type: E27Switch Type: Toggle ButtonComes with bulb','clothes',5,'2022-05-18',NULL,'created','Cherye Tidder','06 Dottie Avenue','1994-01-16','ctidderp8@java.com'),
	 ('Roseanne Simonin','9 Rockefeller Circle','1992-08-05','rbosankop9@msu.edu','Shower Gel - Green Tea','Calm Restor Refresh Made in Malaysia. Content - 1000ml. This exfoliating scrub gently removes dead skin and will leave your body feeling soft and smooth. Delicately scented with a fragrance of Green Tea.  For Beauty tips, tricks & more visit https://bigbasket.blog/','Beauty & Hygiene',97,'2022-07-17',NULL,'delivery','Roselia Bosanko','76005 Kingsford Lane','2002-05-13','rbosankop9@seattletimes.com');
