	 ('Ephrayim Carpenter','914 Mandrake Avenue','1994-04-29','rbrandpp@illinois.edu','Pink Grapefruit & Vitamin C Luxury Shower Gel','St Botanica Pink Grapefruit & Vitamin C Body Wash is a balanced blend of luxurious cleansers and essential oils. Designed for men and women to be used as a body wash, shower gel, or bubble bath. This clinical-grade formula is safe for all skin types and even sensitive skin. Soap-Free and Free from Paraben. St Botanica Pink Grapefruit & Vitamin C Body Wash showers you with the clean, fresh scent of pink grapefruit and vitamin c essential oils, along with skin-conditioning, leaving your skin feeling fresh and delightfully fragrant. St Botanica products offer great quality beauty solutions for the entire family to help you look good, smell good and feel good every day. A unique, high-quality product based on the best, natural, active plant-based ingredients for skin care - created according to timeless Thai spa and healing formulas designed to nourish and heal your skin and senses.','Beauty & Hygiene',75,'2022-05-30',NULL,'created','Reynold Brand','34908 Esch Circle','1993-07-28','rbrandpp@fda.gov'),
	 ('Devin Marages','0943 Blue Bill Park Avenue','2003-02-20','dwhitesidepq@umich.edu','HandMade Gold Plated Cut-Out Sterling Silver Drop Earrings','A pair of gold plated Sterling silver drop earrings with cut-out detail throughout, has a central synthetic pearl dropSecured with a fish-hook ear wire','clothes',94,'2022-07-01','2022-07-02','done','Demeter Whiteside','3940 Merrick Hill','1990-01-22','dwhitesidepq@cbsnews.com'),
	 ('Gabbie Collip','8481 Lien Place','1990-12-28','swestwickpr@dot.gov','Ocean Blue Aroma Bath Salt for Acne Control - Dry Skin & Body Detox','Our mineral-rich sea salt is mined from the Indian Ocean. This natural bath salt draws out impurities from your body, revitalizes skin, eliminates dryness and improves skin texture.','Beauty & Hygiene',83,'2022-10-20',NULL,'created','Sheffie Westwick','1449 Green Ridge Plaza','1991-02-11','swestwickpr@independent.co.uk'),
	 ('Lily Kubista','587 Schlimgen Road','2002-05-14','bbarbrookps@cnet.com','HandMade Boys Black Printed Round Neck T-shirt','Black and Blue Printed T-shirt, has a round neck, short sleeves','clothes',40,'2022-06-05','2022-06-06','done','Bettine Barbrook','59 Mayer Crossing','1999-08-10','bbarbrookps@usnews.com'),
	 ('Paulie Verlander','8258 Becker Park','2004-02-05','npetigrewpt@illinois.edu','Cold Processed Hot Chocolate Handmade Soap','100% pure, natural, vegan and cold-pressed HandMade Hot Chocolate Soap is a handmade, hand-cut, natural oil-based soap. It is made from Chocolate, Cocoa Powder and Cocoa Butter, Coconut milk, oils of Olive, Coconut, Castor and Palm with Vitamin E. Chocolate reduces tan and makes your skin glow while Coconut milk deeply moisturizes your skin. While our exquisite blend of essential oils prevents damage to give you healthy skin. Sensationalize your senses with the lush aroma of our exquisitely blended soap formulation that gives a creamy luxurious lather.','Beauty & Hygiene',17,'2022-05-30',NULL,'delivery','Norean Petigrew','7 Stoughton Terrace','1995-03-09','npetigrewpt@csmonitor.com'),
	 ('Zacharia Lampel','12 North Alley','1996-08-19','voshielspu@storify.com','HandMade Women Green & Mustard Yellow Printed Kurta with Palazzos','Green and mustard yellow  printed kurta with palazzosGreen and mustard yellow straight calf length kurta, has a round neck, three-quarter sleeves, straight hemGreen and mustard yellow printed palazzos, slip-on closure','clothes',28,'2022-05-16','2022-05-19','done','Viviene O''Shiels','778 Sullivan Place','2000-10-09','voshielspu@webeden.co.uk');
INSERT INTO source1.craft_market_wide (craftsman_name,craftsman_address,craftsman_birthday,craftsman_email,product_name,product_description,product_type,product_price,order_created_date,order_completion_date,order_status,customer_name,customer_address,customer_birthday,customer_email) VALUES
	 ('Maryellen Linacre','55 Nova Street','1998-12-26','tgregspv@fema.gov','Almond Oil Scrub Natural Handmade Herbal Soap','Have your baby skin back with Almond Oil Scrub Natural Handmade Herbal Soap from HandMade. Almond oil is a rich source of Vitamins A, B, and E which are great for your skin health. It is really mild on your skin and suits all skin types. It helps in maintaining the moisture levels of your skin and gets absorbed in a jiffy without blocking your pores which we all know is one of the most common reasons behind a number of skin problems. Almond oil is not only a good moisturiser but also works as a great ingredient in scrubs which can help you to get rid of impurities and dead skin. It is also ideal makeup remover for all skin types.','Beauty & Hygiene',36,'2022-07-02',NULL,'created','Trueman Gregs','623 5th Way','1993-07-08','tgregspv@discovery.com'),
	 ('Tadeo Fulkes','16 Pawling Avenue','1999-03-12','nabbettpw@baidu.com','HandMade Women Grey Checked Pencil Skirt','Grey checked pencil skirt, has a waistband, back zipper closure, straight hem.Comes with a belt','clothes',71,'2022-05-31',NULL,'in progress','Noella Abbett','40 Di Loreto Park','2003-11-06','nabbettpw@squidoo.com'),
	 ('Gisele Dewey','66 Lindbergh Alley','1999-05-07','acraciepx@blog.com','Sea Cool Glycerin Soap - Cold Processed, 100% Natural & Organic','Our Sea Cool Glycerin Soap is 100% veg soap, made from natural herbs, essential oils & vegetable oils. Glycerin, which is produced naturally during the soap making process moisturizes the skin. These natural ingredients make our soap bubbly, creamy & soft. Feel refreshed with the amazing aroma of the salty sea.Be on the beach every day! Glycerin has humectants properties, attracting moisture to your skin making it softer & smoother, one of the reasons that our soaps are so beautiful on the skin. This soap does not use any animal product like milk or honey. This product is vegan and is SLS free.','Beauty & Hygiene',26,'2022-06-02',NULL,'in progress','Allegra Cracie','29198 Anderson Way','1991-07-19','acraciepx@loc.gov'),
	 ('Devonna Shutte','6 Mayfield Hill','2004-02-06','speckhampy@delicious.com','HandMade Girls Navy Blue Striped Denim Pinafore Dress','Navy blue and grey striped woven denim pinafore dress, has adjustable shoulder straps, and flared hem','clothes',9,'2022-11-26','2022-11-28','done','Sunny Peckham','3 Coleman Drive','2000-03-08','speckhampy@dedecms.com'),
	 ('Palm Argontt','05 Talmadge Alley','1994-03-25','iauldpz@163.com','Detox Charcoal Shower Gel','This Charcoal detox shower gel is an organic, sulphate-free and mild and deeply purifying formulation enriched with:Charcoal - that is proven to absorb multiple times its own weight in harmful substances like toxins, impurities, bacteria and dirt and helps to fight acne, Black Sand Phytpeel - that deeply exfoliates the skin, Anise - that heals, soothes and adds glow to the skinBasil - that prevents skin infections and rejuvenates the skinLemon - that acts as an antiseptic and astringentNeem - that has anti-bacterial properties for clearer skin and Peppermint - that has a cooling and calming effect on the skin. It reduces sebum and fights off acne producing bacteria and leaves you feeling refreshed and invigorated. It can be used on both face and body.','Beauty & Hygiene',44,'2022-06-17',NULL,'in progress','Isadore Auld','3 Division Alley','1997-05-17','iauldpz@cbslocal.com'),
	 ('Magdaia Monkeman','6 Bultman Park','2000-07-20','bhawsq0@usda.gov','HandMade Gold-Toned & Green Solid Handcrafted Table Lamp with Shade','Type: Handcrafted Table Lamp with ShadeColour: Gold-Toned and greenPattern: SolidShape: FrustumShade material: FabricBase material: AluminiumBulb Holder Type: E27Switch Type: Toggle ButtonComes with bulb','clothes',24,'2022-05-07',NULL,'created','Brandyn Haws','3161 Anderson Drive','1996-05-01','bhawsq0@imdb.com'),
	 ('Lyman Sneezum','3087 Gina Court','2004-09-02','piacovinoq1@fastcompany.com','Rose & Jasmine Handmade Luxury Soap','Enjoy a relaxing bath with our handcrafted soap. Rose and jasmine essential oils are blended to produce a sensuous fragrance that instantly invigorates. The essential oils mingle with premium moisturizing carrier oil to provide superior skin care. Your skin is nourished with fatty acids, vitamins and antioxidants as you cleanse.Flower Power: HandMade soap enriched with floral essential oils and real flower will transform your bathroom into a garden. Your body and mind will be enlivened by rose, jasmine and rhododendron. We have incorporated these amazing flowers and their essential oils into our soap so that your skin is rejuvenated by their antimicrobial, antioxidant and anti-inflammatory properties. They soothe the skin, thwart activities of free radicals, maintain oil balance and enhance your skin tone.Intense Hydration: Unlike soaps with harsh chemicals, saponified organic extra virgin olive oil as the soap base cleans without drying out the skin. The moisture barrier of the skin is fortified with cold-pressed sesame oil, castor oil and virgin coconut oil. Sesame oil is rich in anti-inflammatory compounds. It gives the skin a healthy glow. Castor oil is an excellent cleanser. It dissolves impurities and boosts skin health.Virgin coconut oil is a source of amazing fats that nourish the skin and lock moisture. Mahua oil is one of the best-kept beauty secrets of India. The antioxidant rich oil is an amazing emollient. Kaolin Clay: Owing to the presence of kaolin clay, the intense moisturizing soap will not leave the skin feeling greasy. Kaolin clay absorbs the excess oil and controls the oil balance of the skin. Your skin will feel soft and hydrated for a long time.Healthy Skin Naturally: When your skin receives nourishment when you cleanse it, it will retain its healthy youthful lustre. The dull dry skin is instantly rejuvenated by using this soap. The damaged skin receives nourishment and heals rapidly. Our soap gives your skin everything it needs to stay healthy. Luxurious natural handcrafted soap with invigorating floral fragrance. Made with the finest ingredients available in nature.','Beauty & Hygiene',85,'2022-06-11','2022-06-12','done','Phaidra Iacovino','1 Mendota Pass','1993-01-12','piacovinoq1@example.com'),
	 ('Janeta Askie','0 Mallard Circle','2002-05-22','vbutterlyq2@oakley.com','HandMade Plus Size Beige Solid Underwired Non Padded Everyday Bra P5022','Beige solid medium-coverage Everyday bra Non Padded and Underwired cut and sew cups with lace insertsRegular straps and back closureBack style: RegularFeature: All Day Comfort','clothes',95,'2022-11-15','2022-11-18','done','Valry Butterly','20 Sloan Avenue','2001-01-23','vbutterlyq2@wordpress.com'),
	 ('Ilse MacTeague','036 Maryland Drive','1999-05-29','agarmanq3@artisteer.com','Soap Pocket - Foamy, Bath Essentials','HandMade Bath Essentials Foamy Soap Pocket is here to bring back the Joy of Bathing!Put your soap in this delicately sewn pocket, it is the new trend. It will make your soap lather four times as much and be of use till the very end.','Beauty & Hygiene',24,'2022-07-03',NULL,'in progress','Anthe Garman','86608 Fremont Center','2003-10-26','agarmanq3@dot.gov'),
	 ('Levon Linster','413 Lawn Trail','2001-12-23','jmckinieq4@cdc.gov','HandMade Men Blue Slim Fit Solid Casual Shirt','Blue solid casual shirt, has a spread collar, long sleeves, button placket,  curved hem, one patch pocket','clothes',9,'2022-12-14',NULL,'in progress','Jobye McKinie','41 South Lane','2002-05-02','jmckinieq4@webs.com');
