	 ('Daisy Mallalieu','858 Anhalt Hill','2000-03-18','rsneathq5@patch.com','Mountain Musk Handmade Soap','It has been rumoured since ancient times that musk fragrance is an aphrodisiac. This fragrance adds a touch of sensuality and warmth to the soap and is loved by men and women alike. The mountain musk is an active base soap from nyassa. The active base is an exclusive and unique blend of six pure and natural carrier oils, essential oils and extracts that go into every nyassa handmade soap, namely aloe vera extract, grape seed extract, honey, cold pressed sweet almond oil, cold pressed wheat germ oil and Vitamin E Acetate. These ingredients work best as moisturisers, healers and soothing agents. Apart from the active base, mountain musk contains honeysuckle extract and argan oil extracts. The added ingredients work as anti-bacterial and anti-oxidant agents that help to nourish and soften the skin.','Beauty & Hygiene',80,'2022-09-23',NULL,'created','Rowney Sneath','3 Calypso Alley','2002-07-23','rsneathq5@biblegateway.com'),
	 ('Read Whal','570 Clove Court','2003-10-12','hjevonsq6@umich.edu','HandMade Men Green Solid Polo Collar T-shirt','Green solid T-shirt, has polo collar, short sleeves, one pocket','clothes',15,'2022-11-12','2022-11-15','done','Haydon Jevons','1377 Meadow Valley Way','1995-11-23','hjevonsq6@yelp.com'),
	 ('Eolande Hubbard','64943 Nobel Parkway','2002-05-14','ccapeq7@washington.edu','Brightening Booster Orange Shower Gel','Escape to the shower for an ultimate bathing experience. This naturally soothing orange shower gel is infused with gentle foaming body cleanser and conditioner. The aromatherapy blend of essential oil will pamper your skin and leave it wonderfully scented and rejuvenated.','Beauty & Hygiene',51,'2022-09-04',NULL,'created','Candace Cape','075 Rusk Alley','1997-02-28','ccapeq7@sogou.com'),
	 ('Charmion Christescu','34207 Forest Run Park','1999-04-22','rrisbridgeq8@nasa.gov','HandMade Women Cream-Coloured Solid Peep Toe Flats','A pair of cream-coloured open-toed flats, has regular styling, buckle detailSynthetic upperCushioned footbedTextured and patterned outsoleWarranty: 45 daysWarranty provided by brand/manufacturer','clothes',98,'2022-10-22',NULL,'delivery','Riannon Risbridge','6174 Hoepker Park','2003-03-07','rrisbridgeq8@upenn.edu'),
	 ('Cecilius Mewitt','47042 Northview Terrace','2000-06-25','jlowingq9@shutterfly.com','Purple Delight Shampoo & Shower Gel','Purple Delight Shampoo & Shower Gel contains the extracts of cocoa and glycerine to repair and soften your skin with every wash. It is a unique 2-in-1 product that nourishes both the hair and skin. It gently cleanses skin and hair without ever stripping the natural oils.','Beauty & Hygiene',99,'2022-11-21',NULL,'created','Jessee Lowing','164 Lakewood Gardens Way','1991-01-12','jlowingq9@sitemeter.com'),
	 ('Shanna Confait','446 Sachs Court','1990-12-08','bmccartyqa@pcworld.com','HandMade Absolute Matte Melt Liquid Lip Colour 19 Red Vibe','HandMade Absolute Matte Melt Liquid Lip ColorShade name: 19 Red Vibe','clothes',87,'2022-12-14',NULL,'delivery','Benedicto McCarty','3798 Crownhardt Park','2003-03-16','bmccartyqa@soundcloud.com'),
	 ('Salvidor Tungay','34 Porter Avenue','2002-06-28','jhannqb@pagesperso-orange.fr','Deep Cleansing Soap - With Charcoal, Shea Butter & Wheat Germ Oil','A deep cleansing & detoxifying bar with benefits of activated charcoal & moisturizing qualities of shea butter & wheat germ oil to draw impurities & toxins from deep within pores. This soap contains no harsh chemicals. It is an ayurvedic formulation with researched and useful ingredients. 1. The Packaging: This is a large 125 gm soap that lasts you longer. It comes with a beautiful slider box to ensure you feel great receiving the product- whether for personal use or gifting. 2. The No''s: No Sulfates, No Parabens, No EDTA and No Testing on Animals. 3. The HandMade Promise: All our products are made in small batches. We''re careful of what goes into our products, and understand that only the best','Beauty & Hygiene',34,'2022-10-18',NULL,'in progress','Jackson Hann','9880 Sauthoff Point','2003-04-01','jhannqb@google.ca'),
	 ('Jackqueline Royse','8160 Rockefeller Crossing','2001-11-05','vlembrickqc@nyu.edu','HandMade Plus Size Dusty Pink Solid Underwired Non Padded Everyday Bra P5412','Dusty pink solid medium-coverage Everyday bra with lace inserts detailingNon Padded and Underwired cut and sew cupsRegular straps and back closureBack style: RegularFeature: All Day Comfort','clothes',88,'2022-10-15',NULL,'created','Vernon Lembrick','4711 Gerald Park','1991-05-20','vlembrickqc@ehow.com'),
	 ('Christoph Messent','24 Kingsford Street','1991-01-14','gairesqd@altervista.org','Premium Aloe Hand Wash','Premium Aloe Hand WashHand Wash with lemon clean and refreshed, it features natural ingredients. Honey leaves the hand smooth and supple without harsh cleaning.','Beauty & Hygiene',69,'2022-11-19',NULL,'delivery','Grace Aires','113 Warbler Crossing','1991-07-10','gairesqd@fc2.com'),
	 ('Zachariah Gooderidge','9 Vahlen Alley','1990-03-27','kkeenqe@jimdo.com','HandMade Women Blue Alicia Super Skinny Fit Low-Rise Clean Look Stretchable Ankle Jeans','Blue dark wash 5-pocket low-rise jeans, clean look, no fade, has a button and zip closure, and waistband with belt loops','clothes',88,'2022-05-12','2022-05-15','done','Katharine Keen','5059 Rusk Alley','1990-10-28','kkeenqe@cbsnews.com');
INSERT INTO source1.craft_market_wide (craftsman_name,craftsman_address,craftsman_birthday,craftsman_email,product_name,product_description,product_type,product_price,order_created_date,order_completion_date,order_status,customer_name,customer_address,customer_birthday,customer_email) VALUES
	 ('Ingamar Donnelly','8 David Crossing','1996-07-15','asnedenqf@constantcontact.com','Berry Berry Handmade Sugar Soap','It''s a pure fruity delight. Imagine succulent red raspberries and black currants coming together to make this fruit delight. This fragrance is loved by girls! Delightful in the summer. Berry berry is an active base soap from HandMade. Active base is an exclusive and unique blend of six pure and natural carrier oils, essential oils and extracts that go into every HandMade handmade soap, namely aloe vera extract, grape seed extract, honey, cold pressed sweet almond oil, cold pressed wheat germ oil and Vitamin E Acetate. These ingredients work best as moisturisers, healers and soothing agents. HandMade''s delicious berry berry soap contains three additional ingredients namely strawberry extracts, shea butter and raw cane sugar. Strawberry extracts is a natural softening, toning and moisturising agent. It keeps your skin supple and healthy for long. Shea butter is high in Vitamin A and E, this is a natural moisturiser and sun protectant, keeping skin bright and lustrous. Raw cane sugar contains glycolic acid that helps condition and moisturises the skin.','Beauty & Hygiene',98,'2022-09-13',NULL,'delivery','Averil Sneden','7659 Oakridge Point','1993-10-09','asnedenqf@issuu.com'),
	 ('Westbrook Channon','18 Lien Plaza','2000-12-28','aboordqg@google.com.br','HandMade Men Grey & White Standard Regular Fit Camouflage Print Casual Shirt','Grey, white and black printed casual shirt, has a spread collar, long sleeves, button placket, and curved hem','clothes',67,'2022-11-30',NULL,'delivery','Ancell Boord','05 Donald Parkway','1996-01-17','aboordqg@timesonline.co.uk'),
	 ('Mandie Elms','4581 Di Loreto Junction','2000-12-29','brevettqh@chicagotribune.com','Orange Burst Handmade Loofah Soap','This bar smells like freshly squeezed orange juice. Absolutely delightful, juicy and sweet. HandMades loofah soap brings together effective and natural exfoliating action and invigorating fragrance to give you a truly beneficial and luxurious bathing experience. So, after a tiring and busy day at work or home, feel the magic of HandMade''s natural loofah soap - a product of heaven and earth. Loofah is a wonderful exfoliating natural sponge that gently removes the surface layer of dead skin cells, leaving your skin radiant, healthy and smooth. This exfoliation enhances circulation, removes calluses and gives a healthy glow to the skin. However, this soap is not recommended for individuals with very sensitive skin.','Beauty & Hygiene',88,'2022-06-05',NULL,'in progress','Billi Revett','91 Monument Plaza','1997-06-07','brevettqh@ning.com'),
	 ('Nesta Jacobowits','80989 Maywood Center','2002-01-11','kpearmineqi@skyrock.com','HandMade Boys Pink Printed Comfort Sandals','A pair of pink printed comfort sandalsSynthetic upper with Velcro closureCushioned footbedPatterned rubber outsole','clothes',46,'2022-11-15',NULL,'delivery','Karine Pearmine','6 Buena Vista Junction','1996-07-27','kpearmineqi@unc.edu'),
	 ('Robbie Templeton','2607 Welch Crossing','2000-08-28','egoldbyqj@eventbrite.com','Patchouli & Vetiver Soap','Inatur Herbals Patchouli & Vetiver is a regenerative and relaxing handmade soap prepared in a traditional manner. It has a rich, sweet, herbaceous, aromatic, spicy, woody balsamic note that is excellent for all skin types. Butter and Sugar are added as a base to it to help retain and replenish moisture in the skin. It contains essential oils that are especially recommended for men.','Beauty & Hygiene',40,'2022-07-31','2022-08-02','done','Emmit Goldby','06491 Sunnyside Crossing','1998-04-07','egoldbyqj@hud.gov'),
	 ('Hebert Torri','40 Badeau Pass','1993-05-29','cperviewqk@amazon.co.jp','HandMade Black Geometric Cufflinks','A pair of black and peach-coloured geometric embellished cufflinksComes in a signature HandMade case','clothes',40,'2022-05-04',NULL,'delivery','Cort Perview','393 Armistice Street','1999-04-22','cperviewqk@wp.com'),
	 ('Nelie Kellock','4 Granby Park','2000-11-27','bbowlerql@1688.com','Shower Sponge - Blue/White, Colour May Vary','HandMade shower sponge 9 knots rope features mesh braids, can be stretched conveniently while using. Apply shower gel or soap for easy exfoliation and lather. The braided mesh straps have grip cords on both ends to stretch the braid across hard to reach back and shoulder areas. Rinse and air dry after the bath.','Beauty & Hygiene',93,'2022-05-30',NULL,'in progress','Brandie Bowler','76199 Huxley Park','1998-04-25','bbowlerql@rakuten.co.jp'),
	 ('Alix Burger','9 Florence Park','1994-05-01','schiplinqm@acquirethisname.com','HandMade Unisex Silver Large Trolley Bag','Silver textured large trolley bag, secured with a TSA lockOne handle on the top and one on the side, has a trolley with a retractable handle on the top and four corner mounted inline skate wheelsOne main zip compartment, an inner mesh zip compartment, two compression straps with click clasps and one zip compartment on the flap with a zip pocketWarranty: 5 yearsWarranty provided by Brand Owner / Manufacturer','clothes',53,'2022-08-26',NULL,'created','Sheffy Chiplin','2 Fisk Way','1996-05-16','schiplinqm@ibm.com'),
	 ('Caroljean Pantone','26 Claremont Crossing','2004-12-15','jchinaqn@ted.com','Loofah/Sponge Scrubber/Body Bath - Dual Side, Hangable, Blue, BH-063','This loofah/scrubber is perfect for hard to reach body parts. It is perfect for cleaning back, neck, feet etc. Just hold the loofah from the ends and gently scrub your body. It helps in improving your skin''s blood circulation and eliminates the dead skin cells. It is made of cloth fibres that exfoliate the skin, resulting in the smooth and glowing skin.','Beauty & Hygiene',42,'2022-10-11',NULL,'in progress','Jaimie China','96772 Lawn Street','1992-05-17','jchinaqn@dot.gov'),
	 ('Pascale Stainton','6 Arrowood Alley','1998-03-22','sbreensqo@godaddy.com','HandMade Unisex Black & Grey Printed Large Trolley Bag','Black textured large trolley bag, secured with a TSA lockOne handle on the top and one on the side, has a trolley with a retractable handle on the top and four corner mounted inline skate wheelsOne main zip compartment, zip lining, two compression straps with click clasps and one zip pocketWarranty: 5 yearsWarranty provided by Brand Owner / Manufacturer','clothes',87,'2022-07-31',NULL,'delivery','Sammy Breens','8 Kings Junction','1992-12-27','sbreensqo@epa.gov');
