	 ('Modestia Medwell','4 Northwestern Circle','2001-07-16','ashasnanqp@topsy.com','Cold Processed Papaya Cucumber Handmade Soap','100% pure, natural, vegan, cold-pressed and SLS free, HandMade Papaya Cucumber Soap is a handmade hand cut natural oil-based soap. This soap removes makeup, impurities and improves skin texture giving you smooth and radiant skin. Fresh papaya, aloe vera gel, cucumber which gives your skin a natural and radiant glow. Lighten and brighten your skin with the refreshing aroma and snowy white lather of this soap.','Beauty & Hygiene',47,'2022-11-02',NULL,'delivery','Alexandr Shasnan','9 Evergreen Terrace','1996-10-26','ashasnanqp@hibu.com'),
