	 ('Kakalina Arden','6 Fieldstone Street','1998-02-02','fvernerqs@house.gov','Black Slim Fit Mid-Rise Clean Look Jeans','Get in touch with your feminine side as you wear these jeans, in black colour, from the house of HandMade. Try this pair of jeans that would never let you compromise on both style and comfort. Featuring a distinctive design and pattern, these comfortable jeans will not fail to catch your fancy at a single glance.','clothes',36,'2022-09-19','2022-09-22','done','Ferrel Verner','7084 Fordem Lane','1997-11-28','fvernerqs@ftc.gov'),
	 ('Zelig Touhig','9346 Manitowish Plaza','1995-01-21','kbickstethqt@walmart.com','Papaya & Coconut Bathing Soap','Inatur Papaya & Coconut Bathing Bar is subplate free and 100% soap-free. PH balanced bathing bar containing Coconut oil, Glycerin, Shea butter, and Papaya extracts, for a rich bathing experience that also helps in skin whitening. It emanates a pleasant aroma that instantly uplifts your mood. It has a lingering fragrance and removes any kind of impurity from the skin and soothes allergies.','Beauty & Hygiene',76,'2022-11-12','2022-11-14','done','Karilynn Bicksteth','792 Helena Point','2000-10-29','kbickstethqt@github.io'),
	 ('Kaleb Farmloe','57336 Washington Place','1993-02-02','fdabbsqu@washington.edu','HandMade Men Blue Slip-On Leather Sneakers','A pair of square toe blue slip-on sneakers, has regular styling, slip-on detailLeather upperCushioned footbedTextured and patterned outsoleWarranty: 3 monthsWarranty provided by brand/manufacturer','clothes',17,'2022-07-10',NULL,'created','Floyd Dabbs','2634 Scoville Alley','2000-08-27','fdabbsqu@symantec.com'),
	 ('Felizio Sugarman','641 Alpine Park','1992-09-11','fgrolmannqv@google.co.uk','Tea Tree Body Wash','This Tea Tree Body Wash is made with Australian tea tree oil to gently cleanse the skin without stripping its natural moisture. The anti-bacterial and anti-fungal formulation reduces blemishes with regular use.','Beauty & Hygiene',32,'2022-05-25',NULL,'created','Field Grolmann','84 Ramsey Crossing','2002-07-13','fgrolmannqv@about.com'),
	 ('Hanson MacTrustam','04764 Corben Pass','2000-01-06','ppiscopielloqw@spotify.com','HandMade Men Grey Regular Fit Solid Regular Trousers','Grey solid mid-rise regular trousers, has a button closure, four pockets','clothes',97,'2022-12-23',NULL,'in progress','Pasquale Piscopiello','04 Glendale Place','1996-10-15','ppiscopielloqw@storify.com'),
	 ('Pier Smallman','8805 Muir Alley','1998-12-03','kaldgateqx@nsw.gov.au','Madurai Jasmine & Mogra Handmade Luxury Soap','The sweet seductive fragrance of jasmine has always enchanted people of all ages. By blending the essential oils of two most aromatic jasmine cultivars popular in India, Madurai Jasmine & Mogra, in our handmade soap, we are welcoming you to enjoy a blissful shower experience. HandMade handmade soap assures a rejuvenating bath time. Made with premium ingredients procured from the finest natural sources and eliminating chemicals from our products we have created amazing handcrafted soap that not only purges your skin but also provides intense hydration and superior nourishment. Madurai Jasmine & Mogra: Madurai jasmine, also known as Madurai Malli, is a jasmine cultivar that originated in Madurai in Tamil Nadu. You will never find a woman in Tamil Nadu who had never adorned her tresses with garlands of Madurai jasmine. Mogra is another jasmine cultivar popular across India. The sweetly scented mogra, also known as Jui, Chameli or Mallika, is believed to be the favourite flower of Goddess Laxmi and God Vishnu. The essential oil of jasmine flower has a sweet heady fragrance. It relieves stress, anxiety and increases mental alertness. Furthermore, when used for skin care, jasmine essential oil soothes the skin, restores oil balance, reduces dark spots and pigmentation and slows down skin ageing. Rose Petals: In addition to its sweet fragrance, rose possesses antiseptic, anti-inflammatory and anti-ageing properties. Adding rose petals to the bathwater has always been a part of luxury bath rituals. It soothes the skin and leaves it nourished and healthy.Natural Plant-Based Emollients: With multiple premium plant oils and butter present in the soap, your skin will not only retain its healthy oil balance but its moisture barrier will be strengthened by cleansing with this soap. Plant oils produced through the cold-pressed extraction method are loaded with skin-friendly nutrients. Shea butter soothes the skin and keeps it hydrated for a longer time. Aloe Vera gel helps in healing the damaged skin. Vitamin E: To minimize free radical-induced cell damage we have included vitamin E in our soap formula. Vitamin E preserves the skin’s elasticity and fortifies the moisture barrier. Your skin will retain its youthful appearance. Luxury handcrafted soap made with the finest natural ingredients. Chemical free. Suitable for all skin types.','Beauty & Hygiene',2,'2022-09-12','2022-09-15','done','Kiri Aldgate','0 Almo Trail','1996-09-21','kaldgateqx@cyberchimps.com'),
	 ('Janeta Turn','403 Waywood Street','1996-04-22','tleyburnqy@nasa.gov','HandMade Blue & Grey Geometric 210 TC Cotton 1 King Bedsheet with 2 Pillow Covers','Set content: 1 King bedsheet with 2 pillow coversQuality: RegularThread count: 210Colour: Blue and GreyPattern: Geometric','clothes',64,'2022-06-13',NULL,'in progress','Tobiah Leyburn','735 Wayridge Street','2000-10-18','tleyburnqy@auda.org.au');
