	 ('Elfrieda Treasaden','74291 Vidon Alley','1998-01-27','gdalescor7@nifty.com','Soap Gift Set','This exquisite collection of 9 soaps is an eclectic assortment from the best of HandMade. An indulgence for yourself or for someone you love, this is truly a gift from heaven and earth. HandMade offers this set of 9 handmade soaps that will serve as an excellent gift. Enriched with natural extracts, these soaps will make her skin soft, supple and radiant than ever. Each soap in this set comes in a 25 gm pack.','Beauty & Hygiene',5,'2022-07-29',NULL,'delivery','Gian D''Alesco','49755 Ruskin Park','1994-06-05','gdalescor7@soundcloud.com'),
	 ('Axe Driussi','700 Nobel Plaza','2000-07-10','wselbachr8@dyndns.org','HandMade Green & Orange Printed Table Runner','Set content: One runner Type: Table runner Colour: Green and orange Fabric: Polycotton Shape: Rectangular Pattern: Printed Disclaimer : Product colour may slightly vary due to photographic lighting sources or your monitor settings.','clothes',91,'2022-05-13',NULL,'delivery','Web Selbach','24095 Blaine Hill','1993-04-08','wselbachr8@wikia.com');
