	 ('Sherwin Kehri','3085 Kedzie Circle','1997-01-30','ydeatonr9@alexa.com','Malabar Lemongrass - Invigorating Body Wash','This invigorating lemongrass body wash is made with the steam distilled oil from the finest Lemon grass sourced from the Malabar region in Southern India. The grass is allowed to wilt for 24 hours and the oil is extracted from the wilted herb by steam distillation. Apart from the distinct aroma that imparts it with mood uplifting properties, Lemongrass has multiple anti-microbial and skin friendly properties which have been documented in Ayurveda.','Beauty & Hygiene',57,'2022-07-01',NULL,'created','Yuri Deaton','94 Sutherland Lane','2004-10-29','ydeatonr9@theguardian.com'),
	 ('Pearla Maud','5525 Loftsgordon Lane','1992-04-16','anottonra@adobe.com','HandMade Set of 6 Red & Off White Printed Diwan Set','Set content: One bedsheet with two bolster covers and three cushion covers Bedsheet size: Single Quality: Fine Colour: Red and off-white Print/pattern: Ethnic motifsBolster cover closure: Tie-up Cushion cover closure: Zip','clothes',80,'2022-07-25','2022-07-26','done','Andree Notton','4 Larry Way','1990-09-24','anottonra@wix.com'),
	 ('Sheppard Jowitt','85 Knutson Junction','1995-01-25','wsuattrb@nps.gov','Cold Processed Sweet Rose Handmade Soap For Dry Sensitive Skin','100% pure, natural, vegan and cold-pressed HandMade Sweet Rose Soap is a handmade, hand-cut, natural oil-based soap. Rose Essential oil tightens pores and restores suppleness while rose petals lock in your skin''s moisture to make you glow like never before. Enliven your senses with the sweet aroma of Rose Essential Oil and enhance your bathing experience with the luxurious lather of this soap. It is SLS free.','Beauty & Hygiene',39,'2022-09-07','2022-09-08','done','Wash Suatt','30 Leroy Road','1995-02-04','wsuattrb@boston.com'),
	 ('Vernon Geharke','7106 Mosinee Lane','1997-05-24','sguiserc@webs.com','HandMade Men Grey Solid Bomber Jacket','Grey solid bomber jacket, has a mandarin collar, 2 pockets, zip closure, long sleeves, straight hem, and polyester','clothes',97,'2022-12-22',NULL,'created','Shelley Guise','3 Norway Maple Point','1993-06-11','sguiserc@sciencedaily.com'),
	 ('Michel Foresight','00 Oak Valley Place','1994-06-11','habsolomrd@eepurl.com','Pure Strawberry Glycerin Soap - Cold Processed, 100% Natural & Organic','Fresh Strawberries cleanse skin and help in curing acne and pimples. Packed with Antioxidants, which fight the damaging effects of the sun and environment. Glycerin has Humectants properties, attracting moisture to our skin making it softer & smoother, one of the reasons that our soaps are so beautiful on the skin. This soap does not use any animal product like milk or honey. It is completely vegan and is SLS free.','Beauty & Hygiene',48,'2022-07-16','2022-07-17','done','Hortensia Absolom','7 Monument Center','2000-09-23','habsolomrd@shareasale.com'),
	 ('Jacintha Tichelaar','25926 Weeping Birch Point','2004-04-18','cbeamanre@shop-pro.jp','HandMade Kadee  Women Multicoloured Printed Slip-On','A pair of multicoloured printed flip flopsCroslite upper materialCushioned footbedPatterned synthetic outsoleWarranty: 3 monthsWarranty provided by brand/manufacturer','clothes',69,'2022-08-11',NULL,'created','Caitlin Beaman','2 Sutherland Point','1997-10-05','cbeamanre@spotify.com'),
	 ('Saraann Monkleigh','97251 Gale Terrace','1993-04-23','rbakerf@acquirethisname.com','Manana Cubana Handmade Soap','It has a woody floral fragrance. A fragrance devoured by men and women alike. Think Cuban cigars, beautiful women and an intoxicating fragrance of rose, all combined in our bar of soap. HandMade Manana Cubana is an active base soap. The active base is an exclusive and unique blend of six pure and natural carrier oils, essential oils and extracts that go into every nyassa handmade soap, namely aloe vera extract, grape seed extract, honey, cold pressed sweet almond oil, cold pressed wheat germ oil and Vitamin E Acetate. These ingredients work best as moisturisers, healers and soothing agents. HandMade intoxicating manana Cubana soap contains two additional ingredients, namely, cinnamon extract and rosehip oil which help to rejuvenate and protects skin from damages.','Beauty & Hygiene',41,'2022-08-04',NULL,'in progress','Rubina Bake','2206 Old Gate Junction','1997-08-21','rbakerf@bigcartel.com'),
	 ('Niels Slayny','640 Ridgeview Pass','1996-06-28','ddenyukhinrg@gravatar.com','HandMade Pink & Green Printed Table Runner','Set content: One runner Type: Table runner Colour: Pink and green Fabric: Polycotton Shape: Rectangular Pattern: Printed Disclaimer : Product colour may slightly vary due to photographic lighting sources or your monitor settings.','clothes',75,'2022-11-02',NULL,'in progress','Dallon Denyukhin','99 Lakeland Junction','2001-04-08','ddenyukhinrg@ed.gov'),
	 ('Kamillah Anthonies','52433 Darwin Junction','1990-04-08','hdroganrh@oakley.com','Nomarks - Antimarks Soap For Normal Skin','It contains the goodness of natural ingredients for marks free glowing skin. It contains almonds to nourish and maintain the youthful skin lustre. It also contains oats powder for refreshing, glowing skin and aloe vera to gently cleanse and moisturize.','Beauty & Hygiene',64,'2022-10-30',NULL,'delivery','Harrie Drogan','31 Warbler Terrace','2001-06-01','hdroganrh@posterous.com'),
	 ('Ber Bosche','754 Arkansas Point','1993-09-06','whyndri@behance.net','HandMade Men Teal Blue & Black Striped Round Neck T-shirt','Teal blue and black striped T-shirt, has a round neck, short sleeves','clothes',75,'2022-08-24',NULL,'in progress','Whitney Hynd','2852 Del Sol Pass','1996-03-10','whyndri@house.gov');
