	 ('Vinni Dishmon','512 Golf Court','1990-07-31','soconnelrj@wired.com','Bentonite Clay Natural Handmade Herbal Soap','Bentonite is also referred to as Montmorillonite. It is one of the most effective and powerful healing clays. Bentonite Clay is composed of aged volcanic ash. The name comes from the largest known deposit of Bentonite Clay located in Fort Benton Wyoming. Bentonite Clay is a unique clay due to its ability to produce an “electrical charge” when hydrated upon contact with the fluid, its electrical components change, giving it the ability to absorb toxins. Bentonite removes toxins, heavy metals, impurities, and chemicals. It has the perfect use for detox.','Beauty & Hygiene',98,'2022-09-05',NULL,'created','Sheri O''Connel','7332 Waywood Alley','2003-11-27','soconnelrj@netscape.com'),
	 ('Rafaela Lynock','517 Farragut Hill','2003-06-30','fgoozeerk@abc.net.au','HandMade Men Maroon Regular Fit Printed Casual Shirt','Maroon printed casual shirt, has a spread collar, long sleeves, button placket, straight hem, and 1 patch pocket','clothes',80,'2022-05-12',NULL,'in progress','Freddi Goozee','25 Dayton Point','2000-09-01','fgoozeerk@surveymonkey.com'),
	 ('Miller Varne','30 Bowman Hill','2003-03-28','sstertrl@dion.ne.jp','Green Apple Handmade Sugar Soap','Green, clean, crisp, a subtle sweet all pervasive fragrance. A recommendation for individuals who like lightly fragranced products. Green apple is an active base soap from HandMade. Active Base is an exclusive and unique blend of six pure and natural carrier oils, essential oils and extracts that go into every HandMade handmade soap, namely aloe vera extract, grape seed extract, honey, cold pressed sweet almond oil, cold pressed wheat germ oil and Vitamin E Acetate. These ingredients work best as moisturisers, healers and soothing agents. HandMade''s delicious green apple sugar soap contains three additional ingredients such as green apple extracts, shea butter, raw cane sugar which helps to improve skin functioning and works against harmful toxins. Green apple extract acts as a natural antiaging element in improving skin texture. Shea butter is high in Vitamin A and E, this is a natural moisturiser and sun protectant, keeping skin bright and lustrous. It also guards against harmful toxins. Raw cane sugar contains glycolic acid that helps condition and moisturises the skin.','Beauty & Hygiene',69,'2022-12-11',NULL,'in progress','Scarlett Stert','993 Superior Circle','2003-10-29','sstertrl@wunderground.com'),
	 ('Madonna McSporon','194 Hudson Court','1996-04-09','kciraldorm@seesaa.net','HandMade Women Silver-Plated CZ-Studded Finger Ring',' Silver-plated CZ-studded butterfly-shaped finger ring ','clothes',23,'2022-06-19',NULL,'in progress','Kakalina Ciraldo','33213 Pepper Wood Crossing','1991-05-24','kciraldorm@sogou.com'),
	 ('Sharity Barnhill','4 Badeau Place','1998-12-16','afeigern@bizjournals.com','Soap - Forest Spice','HandMade Soap in Forest Spice is enriched with Kokum butter, which helps keep your skin soft and moisturised with every wash. Whereas, its unique spicy fragrance helps keep you fresh and fragrant even in the most humid of days.','Beauty & Hygiene',22,'2022-11-20',NULL,'delivery','Adi Feige','47691 Saint Paul Road','1992-11-03','afeigern@deliciousdays.com'),
	 ('Wadsworth Fearn','8433 Barby Place','1999-05-04','peastamro@bloglovin.com','HandMade Men Burgundy Suede Loafers','A pair of round-toe burgundy loafers, has regular styling, slip-on detailSuede upperCushioned footbedTextured and patterned outsoleWarranty: 6 monthsWarranty provided by brand/manufacturer','clothes',60,'2022-05-22',NULL,'delivery','Peg Eastam','94783 Mcguire Way','2000-01-11','peastamro@linkedin.com'),
